story: This whimsical stop-motion musical tells the tale of a utopian city of toys and their relationship to each other as well as their "God," an awkward and distant human man with an average job.

name: 1206. Move Like a Boss
story: Two brothers, living with their widowed mother, discover an old door that leads them to a past where their father was alive. They must reconnect with their mother and solve the mystery of their disappearance.

name: 1207. Santa Hunters
story: Chen Xiaozhou encountered an accident after his breakup, and since then, he has often seen a large group of rubber ducks quacking, which has brought a huge obstacle to Chen Xiaozhou's life. Until the appearance of a girl named Feng Jianan.

name: 1208. De mannenmaker
story: Tomás, an elderly father, has invited his two sons, Jesús and Antonio, to dinner to give them important news about his inheritance and Lina, a girl who is helping him write his biography.

name: 1209. Holly by Nightfall
story: Brothers Fiachra and Tadgh peaked at the age of 7 when they appeared on the TV singing with their homemade puppet, "Froggie". 25 years later, they are still singing the same ol' song - until one day, Froggie is stolen.

name: 1210. Tulang Belulang Tulang
story: Gary is obsessed with a certain flavour of chicken wings. When his favorite restaurant closes and he can't get them anymore his life descends into madness so he goes crazy on a quest searching for Garlic Parmesan chicken wings. Through his journey discovers the difference between being full and being fullfilled. It's a dark meat comedy.

name: 1211. Hep Yek: Asiret
story: Zinnia Flower seeds, which can grow in space, were planted in the botanical area of the Misfits Adventure Park 25 years ago, and this was noticed by the documentary team from USA at the end of the year celebrations of the youth camp.

name: 1212. Paradise: A Town of Sinners and Saints
story: Two different movies are clashing, causing reality to fall into chaos. An immortal hero is leaving a path of destruction on a lighthearted world. It's now up to Ever to find him, and rebel against the higher powers that doomed them.

name: 1213. Buscando a Coque
story: While attempting a love connection, an obnoxious guy gets trapped inside his own coat at a laundromat.

name: 1214. Ismo - maailman hauskin ulkopuolinen
story: Hind, Emy and Rania can't really stand each other. In the 90s, during their university years, they used to sing together in a band in before personal differences tore them apart. When they receive an invitation to sing together in Aswan, the three women reunite and are forced to work together on one last show. As they come together for this surprise reunion, they find themselves in a mix of challenges and comedic moments, remembering their past and rediscovering their present.

name: 1215. CHAAW: Chapter 3 - Christmas Time Is Here
story: A Russian family's Turkish vacation turns chaotic when they can't afford to return home. Pretending to be wealthy to impress old rivals, they dodge hotel staff while living on the edge. Tensions rise as they navigate their predicament.

name: 1216. Double Engine
story: Agus, who is described as an intelligent, agile and tough man, whose behavior is effective in winning the heart of his partner, Kalis. The love story of Agus and Kalis during their courtship will be full of twists and turns.

name: 1217. Les boules de Noël
story: Over a weekend visit in Los Angeles, two first-generation Sierra Leonean American brothers navigate the changing dynamics of brotherhood after a surprise announcement.

name: 1218. Me contro Te: Cattivissimi a Natale
story: The film's narrative revolves around a bed and its three occupants. It follows Rugmangadan, who wakes up in his car and is pursued by goons, but.

name: 1219. Scream: The Fan Favorite
story: A young American in Paris meets a girl with a morbid curiosity for the darker sides of the city's history.

name: 1220. Meen Yasadaq
story: The spirit of Robin Williams comes roaring into the life of a sensitive artist named Roger, who finds himself questioning his sanity but nonetheless mounts a hysterical live tribute to the beloved comic.

name: 1221. Gecenin Nakarati
story: After losing the role of a lifetime, an aspiring actor retreats to his hometown. When he encounters a woman who has Lyme disease, an unexpected friendship develops, forcing them both to make life-altering decisions.

name: 1222. The Million Dollar Bet
story: Three friends, who were fans of Ivanushki International in their youth, meet and decide that they have never done a single crazy thing in their entire lives. They decide to fulfill their old dream and go on a fan tour for "Ivanushki" in the south of Russia, hoping to escape from their problems for a while. But the 15-year-old daughter of one of them ends up traveling with them.

name: 1223. Ducobu passe au vert!
story: During the shooting of a horror movie, an eccentric B-movie producer inadvertently summons a demon.

name: 1224. Home-less for the Holidays
story: When Princess Avali flees her early coronation to a small town and meets Anderson, a famous celebrity look-alike, a viral video causes a comedic identity mix up, having everyone guessing "who's who?"

name: 1225. Reel Hard
story: After being reassigned from music to field reporting, a critic goes to a refugee camp near Paris during an evacuation. He experiences police violence and is thrust into becoming the face of the refugee cause.

name: 1226. Paper Plates
story: A family's challenges as an elder passes away during the inauspicious celestial alignment, characters attempting to defy predictions while reflecting on tradition, belief, and the absurdity of controlling fate.

name: 1227. Darshini
story: Zhenya Horobchik is a Kyiv photographer originally from Zhashkiv who is much loved by women. He is looking for a job, but accidentally finds a new love. Zhenya already has a wife and a son, and an ex-wife and a bunch of problems. He's torn between them and decides he'd rather be under a train than go on like this.

name: 1228. Tratamos demasiado bien a las mujeres
story: Norbert, a 65-year-old from a working-class area, plans a major heist to finance his gender transition surgery.

name: 1229. Kalvan
story: Focuses around Carole, the mayor of a small town, who assists the community's residents with the celebrations as her devoted husband Alain plans the Christmas Eve celebrations at home.

name: 1230. Doctor X: The Movie
story: Rob and Chris own a video shop. But when gangster Clarence donates tapes containing unspeakable evil on, the duo gets entangled in a dangerous game. Now, they must navigate eccentric customers and escape the clutches of organized crime.

name: 1231. Gelin Takimi
story: Manyunya, Narine and Karine go to the village to visit their grandmother for the summer holidays, where they face boring and monotonous days, but unexpected events force them to look at village life in a new way.

name: 1232. Sovsem oshaleli
story: After faking a wedding with her childhood best friend to please her mom's dying wish, Dannie, an insatiable idealist, is faced with a dilemma when her mother is miraculously healed.

name: 1233. Monster Metaverse: Monster Hunter Academy
story: A misunderstanding resulted in MUKIDI being accepted to work as a Credit Analyst. He also approves all credit applications to help many people. Unfortunately, that decision resulted in disaster. Together with his wife, MARKONAH, and his two friends, SAMINGAN and WAKIJAN, Mukidi must clean up the huge losses he caused.

name: 1234. One Day League: Dead Mother, Dead All
story: Marina and Viktor are the only people left in a huge city, perhaps on the entire planet. After the heroes had somehow arranged their daily life, they were faced with a much more serious question - an existential one. How to revive humanity? Especially considering that they don't like each other.

name: 1235. Guy Friends
story: While visiting a village in France, Cecile uncovers the darkest and most exciting secrets of the place.

name: 1236. Odd Fish
story: With the unexpected turn in his life, when an assistant director Raju Sundaram falls into the crime world, he over smarts criminals to escape from a deadly situation. Cinema is the most beautiful Fraud in the world.

name: 1237. Tschugger - Der Lätscht Fall
story: KJ leaves school, unsure if he'll ever return. He arrives home, only to find that his parents have moved without telling him. Directionless, he meets an old friend and joins a ragtag rock band, paving the way for an eventful summer.

name: 1238. V de Victor
story: From the haunted forests of a lost Portuguese village, an evil energy is born - Humanity's only hope is a retired construction worker, a bottle of wine, a Zündapp 50cc motorcycle and a sword possessed by a strange demon.

name: 1239. Eternal Playground
story: The plot unravels with a Professor who comes in search of a treasure and finds himself in a fearful fix and befriends a local villager in order to survive. His motives change with the unusual bond he builds with these simple villagers.

name: 1240. Sleep with Your Eyes Open
story: The carefree Balaraju must transform his roguish ways to earn the love of Mahalakshmi in the town of Sri Rangapuram, despite matriarch Indravathi Patel's disapproval. Can Balaraju's victory overturn societal norms and allow their marriage?

name: 1241. Gone with the Dead
story: An anthology of five short films showcasing Moldova like never before, blending magical journeys, cultural clashes and strange encounters.

name: 1242. City of Second Chances
story: Uncle Yura, serves as a security guard in an elite village, raises a mini-pig Kostya and does not like New Year at all.

name: 1243. Mandakini
story: The struggle of a young man to maintain a family secret amidst some testing situations and poky neighbourhood that leads to funny situations and later to family bonding.

name: 1244. Fruitcake
story: Ivan, a long-haul truck driver, accepts a trip before Christmas, but unexpected adventures put his on-time return home for Christmas in danger.

name: 1245. Road Trip
story: 20-year-old Ousmane Diallo is the new international soccer star. On a night that will mark a turning point in his life, he has to choose which national team he will play for for the rest of his career. [... ]

name: 1246. God's Blessings
story: Donnell Rawlings discusses relationships, travel, aging and parenting while wearing a blue suit, red socks and moisturized ankles.

name: 1247. My Crazy Rich Girlfriend
story: In a single night, a responsible, orderly and controlling woman will be forced to do everything she has not dared to do in thirty-six years.

name: 1248. You, Me and Christmas Makes Three
story: A young circus artist who discovers the world of professional clowns following an injury.

name: 1249. The Trainers
story: 5th grade student Masha Kametova learns that she will be left at home alone for several days because her parents are leaving on an urgent business trip. A nanny was called to look after Masha, who was found through a fashionable online service. However, who would have guessed that a professional nanny had an insidious plan? As soon as Masha realizes this, she decides to use modern gadgets to bring the criminal to light and show her who is boss in the smart home.

name: 1250. Taxi Cab Comedy with Jimmy Failla
story: With help from a recovering combat veteran, an overly optimistic young man and his cranky grandpa set out in a rickety van on a road trip from hell that leads to divine destiny.

name: 1251. Bantay-bahay
story: After the passing of his wife Berna, Macit's hope for a fresh start is put to test by his son Alp and his wife's assistant Feyza, both strongly attached to Berna's legacy.

name: 1252. Muxmäuschenstill X
story: Ustaz Kazim Elias is a beloved religious teacher, but at the same time, there are individuals who are jealous and not satisfied with him, even to the extent of sending him black magic.

name: 1253. Silent Trilogy
story: Following the eccentric tenants of a run-down apartment complex in Niagara Falls.

name: 1254. O nomos tou Merfy
story: When Sean Astin, D. B. Sweeney, Michael Muhney and Jessica Roszko collide, you have a mix of the best short independent films since Sundance. Checkout the finest short films from drama to animation with a little bit of thriller and comedy.

name: 1255. Dirty Laundry
story: Kevin and Mia are con artists, who seduce and rob wealthy women. Their robbery of the wealthy seductress Emma goes awry. In a remote forest, Emma wakes up and flees. They set out to hunt her down. A game of cat and mouse begins.

name: 1256. Just Pass
story: Christmas at a roadkill collection company gets bloody as employees are killed off one by one by an evil reindeer who is dead set on killing them all. Will they figure out who's the killer? Or will they all be Flattened?

name: 1257. Falla girare 2
story: A now-blind athlete must rely on his estranged brother, who may have just used him as an excuse to get himself out of jail. The two were never close, but the brothers soon realized a connection they couldn't always see.

name: 1258. Sundaram Master
story: Radha, a saree draper, falls for Krishna, who's hesitant about intimacy. Seeking wisdom, Radha understands love's depth beyond physical bonds. But Krishna's parents oppose their marriage, disrupting their relationship.

name: 1259. Switched at Death
story: Guest and Staff at the Palm Court Motel have become prey, after a serial killer checks in for the night.

name: 1260. 80 Plus
story: A humble boda boda driver rescues a lonely British woman after she falls for an internet romance scam in Kenya.

name: 1261. My Eyes Only
story: An ex-couple are both set to inherit a lot of money if they can spend the week together in a remote cabin getaway.

name: 1262. Lady Parts
story: Pablo Majumdar, Aditi Mitra, and Swatilekha Sen working in different IT companies cross paths in the professional sphere where a series of events unfold.

name: 1263. Sonnenplätze
story: Three weddings and one funeral in Eastern-Slovak style.

name: 1264. Marlon Wayans: Good Grief
story: Jim marries his first interested partner but after her departure, his friends push him into dating apps where he unexpectedly falls for the second person who showed interest.

name: 1265. The Fall of 2008
story: Since the war started, Ivan Zabiyaka, a former Ukrainian railroad worker from the Kharkiv region, has become erratic. Now, he faces imprisonment unless he leaves. An officer offers freedom, but Ivan has other plans.

name: 1266. Here and Now
story: I made this while going through some stuff - c.

name: 1267. The Heist
story: Wanda and Janek make the final attempt to save their relationship and set off on a journey along the winter coast of the Baltic Sea.

name: 1268. Blue Star
story: A popular female vlogger realizes too late that sharing her life online has, along with some perks, terrible downsides as well. In her constant search for validation, the answer she seeks may just be by simply facing the real world head-on. To add to her rather uneventful life as a social media manager for a company that sells beauty products made in Korea, FATIMA REGALA compensates by being a somewhat famous vlogger.

name: 1269. Thekku Vadakku
story: Two friends decide to start a car washing business together called "Black and White". One of their favourite customers is an old man named Singham who regularly brings his BMW to them. When Singham passes, the boys accept his BMW as a gift, but his ghost comes back to disrupt their grand fantasies.

name: 1270. Sounds Like A Great Project!
story: Three adventurous women are sucked into their game of Dungeons and Dragons (DND) and must fight mythical monsters to win all of the money in the world... or die trying. Together, they learn they can change the rules of the game - and play by their own. Celebrating the 50th Anniversary of Dungeons and Dragons: Happy 50th Birthday DND.

name: 1271. Todo Mundo (Ainda) Tem Problemas Sexuais
story: The situation in the city of Medan is not conducive because there is a feud between five big gangs seeking influence and power. They are the Batak Gang that controls Central Medan, the Javanese Gang that controls North Medan, the Chinese Gang that controls East Medan, the Indian Gang that controls South Medan, and the Malay Gang that controls West Medan. The Chinese Gang Leader wants to match his younger brother, Kenzo, with Indian Gang Leader Rakesh's younger sister Anjali. They secretly want to unite the territories they have previously controlled. However, Binsar, the leader of the Batak Gang, strongly opposed the match.

name: 1272. Athens Midnight Radio
story: Living off past glories, Sérgio Mallandro accepts participating in a pilot for a new TV show after being eliminated from a reality show. When a prank goes wrong, he faces a life-or-death situation and must make a career-altering decision.

name: 1273. Perumani
story: When two strangers cross paths, sparking hilarious misadventures and unexpected feelings. Amid playful banter and quirky situations, love blossoms unpredictably through twists and turns.

name: 1274. Office Madness
story: Kolkata is at risk from Badami Hyena. Dipak Chatterjee, a forgotten detective created by Shri Swapankumar, faces a complex mission. Can he save the city and himself?

name: 1275. Hello My Beautiful Creatures
story: Veeranna builds a Ganesha temple for re-election. Celebrity inauguration derailed by tragic death. Village seeks replacement. Krishnappa's friend Nandish promises CM's presence, giving village hope and making Krishnappa a hero.

name: 1276. Yesterday After Tomorrow
story: Sundar Asopa wanted opulence and contentment in his life but for that his Shukranus must reach the destination so his Shukrdosh can come to an end, but this journey turns out to be a domino effect of disasters for him.

name: 1277. Welcome to My Side
story: Apaixonada, a book by Cris Souza Fontes, follows a woman who faces an identity crisis and embarks on a journey of self-discovery.

name: 1278. La bandera
story: Håkan Bråkan wants a pet, but he has to show that he really is responsible enough. First - a week at a scout Jamboree without causing chaos? But there are thieves and he finds a treasure map to dangerous caves. Can he go for the adventure?

name: 1279. Froggie
story: John, Jonathan and Leonard Diarrhea are delivery drivers for their family business. Winston, a new hire, is swept up in their lives of chaos and diarrhea.

name: 1280. Garlic Parmesan
story: Manu, an artist, is on a mission to get noticed again after advanced printing technology shows up and steals his spotlight. He's trying out modern tricks to be more efficient. Will he make it?

name: 1281. Afacanlar Kampta
story: Li Qingrang, a former street thug, encountered setbacks in his attempts to find a job after being released from prison. An accidental encounter with his old acquaintance Wang Daji led him to join the "Home for Patients" with a conspiracy.

name: 1282. Best Cop Ever
story: A circus-like dark comedy about a country of destruction.

name: 1283. Static Cling
story: In the hands of Mityay, a school geography teacher from Sochi, is not just a talking, but an intelligent parrot from an ancient family. His name is Innokenty - or simply Kesha for his friends. The parrot ends up with Mityay at a difficult moment in his life - his girlfriend Lera puts the relationship on pause. She wants a luxurious life, but Mityay cannot provide it for her. But maybe a parrot. More precisely, he can "pump up" Mityay so that he starts earning a lot. New friends make an agreement - Kesha will help return Mityay to Lera, and Mityay will help the parrot find and return his beloved, from whom they were separated.

name: 1284. Maqsoom
story: Family tensions rise during a domino game where supernatural elements reveal secrets and hidden truths.

name: 1285. Belyakovy v otpuske
story: Emma is a very famous dog on Instagram who stars in Dog food commercials. One day, Alisa, a rich and spoiled girl, tells her father that she will allow him to marry a new woman on the condition if he buys Emma from Atlas.

name: 1286. Seni Memahami Kekasih
story: A misfit horror-themed rock band relocates to rural Japan, determined to compose the ultimate punk anthem.

name: 1287. African Giants
story: A scientist with a brilliant brain builds a humanoid robot. But a series of events leads to thrill and comic situations that create a boomerang effect.

name: 1288. Oru Kattil Oru Muri
story: A guardian ghost saving a girl from all the dangers surrounding her.

name: 1289. Paul and Paulette Take a Bath
story: Ulvi and Cevahir, after a period of separation, reunite due to Ulvi's involvement in a murder case. Cevahir investigates to discovers who has been killing the people in village and framing Ulvi, who is bad at butchering.

name: 1290. Being Robin
story: An American-born Marathi, Samar, travels to India seeking a cultured bride. Excited but clueless, he navigates Indian culture and discovers love plus lessons on identity, acceptance, and roots.

name: 1291. 60 Miles North
story: Teteng, a single father and assistant to a film director, faces his last days due to a brain tumor. Despite his fear of confrontation, he becomes determined to protect his tomboyish daughter Tintin from bullies. Teteng, romantically interested in Tintin's teacher, discovers his illness and gets involved in a bar fight, leading to Tintin's kidnapping by a crime boss. With nothing to lose, Teteng fights relentlessly, showcasing his strength and love for his daughter until his final moments.

name: 1292. Challenger
story: Motu and Patlu decide to participate in the race to help their village's development. Soon after, they land in France, where they face off against talented racers from various parts of the world. Will they emerge victorious?

name: 1293. Tur s Ivanushkami
story: A teen ballerina, her crazy in love boyfriend, and his sketchy best friend with a stolen gun, get stuck in the deepest labyrinths of crime's underworld over a misplaced cell phone that contains a compromising video.

name: 1294. L'amore e altre seghe mentali
story: The lives of gig economy workers intersect as they try to make ends meet in Chicago. A non binary bike messenger delivers sexy toys, two sisters deliver art, and two roommates sell drugs for their friend while he's on vacation.

name: 1295. The Haunted Studio
story: Grief, pandemic isolation and random Lil' Tokyo pigeons inspire a TV writer to rekindle her former BFF-ship.

name: 1296. Royal Façade
story: A man takes an acting exercise too far and must deal with the consequences.

name: 1297. Just a Couple of Days
story: In Kothula Gutta, Shiva dreams beyond his village. When love and fate intertwine, an epic journey of challenges and redemption unfolds.

name: 1298. Panchak
story: Off the heels of "Surge of Dawn" delving further into the devious activities of The Council, Surge has his next team up with guest superhero, The Smoke. Audiences are already familiar with Surge, Omen, MAVIS, Will E. Bee and some members of The Council from previous "Surge of Power" movies, but who is Falling Apple and what is her role in The Council's evil scheme? Struggling from a lifetime of trauma, Falling Apple has discarded her civilian life as Chai Appuru for a gritty life full of anger and resentment as she seeks to exact revenge on those she believes killed her father when she was a child, putting the entire Chicago area in peril. Is Falling Apple's agenda aligned with The Council's goals? Watch as Omen guides Surge in recruiting more "champions" to form a superhero team to face The Council's threat.

name: 1299. Top 10 Must
story: A notorious art thief wanting a different life is involved with two of the biggest organized crime families in Monterey, CA. While trying to find a way out of crime, the masked art thief finds himself on an adventure that could unravel some unsettling relationships.

name: 1300. Don Zhuan iz Zhashkova
story: A group of childhood friends - Zoinhu, Linguinha, Mãodelo, and Alãodelom - manage as best they can by applying small scams and crimes. However, one of them is not satisfied with this life. Zoinhu no longer wants to risk being arrested every day and he knows that, even if everything is difficult now, in jail things will only get worse. Until, one day, there is a chance for the group to reproduce a much more daring criminal scam that seems to give a much higher reward than what they are used to. However, this opportunity is just the beginning of an even bigger mess, as they end up getting into the plans of a gang of a corrupt policeman who begins a relentless search for those who hindered their scheme.

name: 1301. Norbert(a)
story: "Suswagatam Khushamadeed" intends to spread a message of love, friendship and compassion elements that glue a society together. The film will fulfil the much required love , support and humour in this dark times.

name: 1302. Christmas Carole
story: Kalyani loses her job and hatches a questionable scheme with friends to marry a Brit for stability, testing bonds and imperiling relationships, ultimately learning true success springs from courage to face inner fears, not risky shortcuts.

name: 1303. One Night Rental
story: Five struggling coffee shop owners in Trivandrum cross paths with unsavory characters, leading to a thrilling journey of navigating trouble and finding redemption.

name: 1304. Manyunya. Priklyucheniya v derevne
story: During the Covid-19 pandemic, four anxious strangers take a record-breaking dose of LSD, catapulting them into a shared psychedelic dream where they must find solace and redemption before they can return to the real world.

name: 1305. Chicken Factory
story: When a failed guitarist finally decides to leave LA for good, a chance encounter with a ukulele-playing stranger reignites his creative spark.

name: 1306. Ordinary Things
story: Fede is depressed and firmly convinced he has no interest in social life. He meets Iván, and old acquaintance from his childhood who is also kind of blue, and he insists they should provide each other company because even though their lives may seem unremarkable, they can still anticipate plenty of unexpected plot twists in the future.

name: 1307. Mukidi
story: It is the story of a strange and cursed village where the entire young generation is unmarried, Bagheli Superstar Avinash Tiwari plays the lead role in this film as Prem Prakash Parauha (Pappu) and Annapurna Dwivedi as Lalita (Lalli).

name: 1308. Adam i Eva
story: Danny (Spanish) and Ana (Mexican) just started dating in Los Angeles when Danny has to travel to Madrid to renew his visa. He is about to return when the COVID pandemic hits the world making it impossible for him to go back to the US.

name: 1309. We Are Tourists
story: Raja, an Indian immigrant, starts a new job in USA and his first client is far from "ordinary". Chaos ensues as they unravel a dark secret and he is forced to join hands with a man named 420 (Fraudster) to escape this thrilling situation.

name: 1310. Bharathanatyam
story: A group of politically motivated labor lawyers hides in a house when the coup d'état of February 23, 1981 takes place in Spain. Without really knowing what to do.

name: 1311. Mustard Man
story: Unemployed and up to her eyeballs in debt, Armande Pigeon (26) is struggling in Brussels. On top of that, she has a penchant for gambling and doesn't hesitate to take risks because for Armande, all bets are good. All except one, perhaps the craziest bet she is still struggling to take: love.

name: 1312. The Old Man and the Demon Sword
story: A renowned photographer and an inexperienced journalist visit a decadent high society country club in São Paulo where gender stereotypes are reversed for interviews but trouble ensues after three lions escape their cages.

name: 1313. Babe Mansion
story: A member of the Mexican Army fell into a coma during a battle, when he wakes up he discovers that his wife has married a drug lord and his son is his lieutenant, refusing to accept this, he decides to get his son out of that criminal life.

name: 1314. Buffalo Travels
story: A heartbroken 20-something reluctantly returns to his childhood home in Miami, where he's forced to reevaluate his relationships in the face of a looming hurricane.

name: 1315. Bootcut Balaraju
story: Rock Randall and his writing partner Doris Adams are desperate to break away from the drab routine of writing television sitcoms in order to focus on creating a feature film script. Freeman, their TV producer, bets them they can't come up with a good screenplay in a single night while stashed in an out-of-the-way rural house. Rock and Doris take the bet and hole up in the house, but before they can get started creating, the place is invaded by a wild variety of strange characters, all of whom seem involved in thievery, chicanery, and murder. Before Rock and Doris can write their movie, they have to solve the mystery of the house they're writing it in.

name: 1316. Povesti Moldovenesti
story: Demi and Kanla are living the dream. Their fashion business is booming, and their friendship bond is unbreakable. However, things take a different turn when they both fall in love with Mbali, a beautiful woman who enters their lives like a whirlwind. Initially unaware of their feelings, Mbali becomes the object of their affection, setting the stage for an intense love triangle.

name: 1317. Yolki 11
story: A gardener (Oldrich Kaiser) and his wife live at the foot of a picturesque hill and take care of their small garden. Their idyllic life will be disrupted by a new owner, .

name: 1318. Bharathanatyam
story: In a world where housing prices are sky-high, Patrick must choose: buy a house or live in his van forever. "Opportunity" follows his journey through crime and chaos battling Mormon gangsters with his friend Donnie.

name: 1319. The Truck
story: A fable about musician Abdo, who rebels against his elders, seeking freedom through his art in a confined world outside of time.

name: 1320. Numéro 10
story: Two brothers turn their uncles' luxurious house into a motel for an entire summer.

name: 1321. Chappelle's Home Team: Donnell Rawlings - A New Day
story: Devi grew up with her mother and believed her father was the famous Indian actor, Amitabh Bachchan. Living in Kerinci, she was often teased by people, because she dressed in Indian style.

name: 1322. Un mal día lo tiene cualquiera
story: A dark comedy showcasing the wide variety of evil behaviour human beings are capable of.

name: 1323. Sur un fil
story: Salvador Dalí receives a visit from a journalist who wants to interview him about the sudden reappearance of a book that the painter wrote 20 years ago and that was lost during his flight during the Nazi invasion of France.

name: 1324. Ne odna doma
story: After Ivy's parents were killed when he was a kid, it spawned a bitter relationship with God. Living in an overwhelmingly Christian town, his only purpose is caring for his terminally ill, pot-smoking Aunt. But when Ivy falls for the new local preacher's daughter, Sadie, he can't help but convince her he's a big fan of Jesus. That lie snowballs when his anarchist friend agrees to coach Ivy how to pose as a Christian, with the agreement Ivy will provide insider information on the Church's fund-raising. As Ivy's lie helps him grow closer to Sadie, it inadvertently plants a seed of optimism. Will he be exposed or actually come to terms with his disdain for whoever is up there wrecking his life?

name: 1325. Miracle Mile
story: Kemal, who lost his wife at an early age, lives with his two daughters, Ceren and Beren. Kemal decides to take a woman into his life, thinking that his daughters will marry and leave in the future.

name: 1326. The Grand Siege
story: A small-time thief inadvertently steals a car with an 8-year-old boy in the backseat.

name: 1327. Zim Zim Ala Kazim
story: The journey of a struggling young pilot, Kai, and his fighter mecha, Little Dragon, set against a backdrop of epic galactic warfare told with action, humor, and heart, rekindling wonder in adults and sparking the imaginations of children.

name: 1328. The Legacy of Cloudy Falls
story: It is a fun filled story of two middle aged fathers who are rivals according to their cultures , and when their children falls in love and tries their hardest subsequently in a simple and crazy way to bring them together to make their marriage happen in a peaceful way .

name: 1329. Spotlight International Film Festival: Best of the Festival - Volume 1
story: After losing his fortune, a wealthy patriarch must accept a loaned Corsican villa for his family's summer getaway. Their usual luxury is replaced by an authentic Corsican experience, with their overstayed son and visiting daughter in tow.

name: 1330. Jama
story: Mike Epps reflects on his career success and personal struggles, touching on financial issues, relationships, and his signature comedic takes on life in the streets.

name: 1331. A Very Flattened Christmas
story: From his thoughts on aggressively scented trash bags to desk jobs in hell, Demetri Martin returns with a new stand-up special.

name: 1332. My Annoying Brother
story: Omar gets a job as a driver for the family and in between becomes the nanny of the girl Anfisa. At first glance, it seems that she lives in paradise: her parents have a lot of money, and the house looks like a museum and has artificial intelligence. In fact, the marriage of her mother and father is bursting at the seams, and Anfisa herself is trying in every possible way to prevent their divorce, doing unimaginable tricks. The main character has his own reasons for enduring the antics of the obnoxious girl: he needs a luxurious house to pose as a millionaire in front of his relatives who are about to arrive from Dagestan. Meanwhile, the previously fired family tutor Valeriy conceived an insidious plan that could destroy the lives of all the people involved.

name: 1333. Bhale Unnade
story: Vanessa is kidnapped once again. this time by a new Mutant on the streets that goes by the name of Black Cage, who is out for revenge. Now Deadpool must put his team together and fight for Vanessa's life before it's too late.

name: 1334. The Inn
story: Cata dumps her lazy boyfriend with the secret hope that he will return, begging to get back together. When time passes and she doesn't hear from him, a devastated Cata heads off to a luxury beach resort. But who should she find there, but her lazy ex, now transformed into the perfect man... and ready to marry someone else.

name: 1335. Boda Love
story: A struggling single mom takes a temp job with an aging movie star and teams up with the star's chauffeur to stop a scheming lawyer and agent from stealing her fortune, finding love and holiday magic along the way.
Two struggling brothers in Marrakech scheme to win the favor of a wealthy woman to fund their dream of opening a restaurant, while navigating financial troubles and past mistakes.

name: 1337. Inheritance to Love
story: Lin Yao has loved practicing martial arts since he was a child and thought he was very powerful. After experiencing deception and betrayal, he recognized who he was, regained confidence, practiced drunken boxing, and became a true hero.

name: 1338. Alaap
story: Serra and Erdem are a young couple who cannot make their marriage work. When they decide to divorce, they announce this situation to all their friends at a party. But Serra's family cannot accept this.

name: 1339. Kavej
story: The movie is inspired by the uncomfortable fact that although MLK BLVD was meant to honor the life and legacy of Rev. Dr. Martin Luther King Jr, many MLK BLVD streets in the USA are located in blighted neighborhoods. The movie is about a young man who lives on MLK BLVD and attempts to transform his community into a place that really honors Dr. King. Joining him on his important and hilarious journey are old friends and new allies.

name: 1340. Near Miss
story: Luiz Antônio, a clumsy radio host, unexpectedly finds himself in charge of a bankrupt radio station. With a very crazy team, he creates one of the most emblematic radio stations in the history of Brazilian rock, Fluminense FM.

name: 1341. The Eggsplosive Easter
story: A grandfather decides to launch a childcare business alongside a bitter divorcee who is also an aging game show icon trying to make a comeback.

name: 1342. The Hero's Journey aka My Life aka the Caleb Johnston Story (I'm Caleb)
story: A young woman's heart is torn between her musician boyfriend who is on the brink of fame, and a man who understands her more than anyone.

name: 1343. To nie mój film
story: Lucy and Belle are two Pomeranian sisters. They have been left at home to guard the house over the Christmas period with two children. However - all does not go to plan when two neighbours break in to steal the family's possessions.

name: 1344. Girl Online
story: Four chaotic sisters have to save a dancing penguin from evil magicians who want to use him for their comeback show in Las Vegas.

name: 1345. Black & White
story: The retired parents are about to move to Spain - as soon as the father tells his employer to stop working as a taxi driver. However, the father's plans are revolutionized in one fell swoop, when the host acquires a new ride for his taxi company, a luxury class Mersu with all the goodies.

name: 1346. DND Betches!
story: An unemployed actress tries to run away from Christmas but is offered a commercial by a lonely ad executive if she can convince his Christmas-obsessed staff to finish an ad campaign on Christmas Eve.

name: 1347. Negeri Para Ketua
story: One widow, two wives, three families and... a stork.

name: 1348. Mallandro: O Errado que Deu Certo
story: Xue Ming was originally a person without great ambitions, but he became a big hero in the small town after fighting a fire while drunk. But Xue Ming knew he was fake, the real rescuer's life was in danger. The condemnation of conscience made Xue Ming resolutely speak the truth. He went from a great hero to a great fraud, and Xue Ming decided to use the heat to raise funds for the true hero, finally becoming his own hero.

name: 1349. Miya Biwi Raazi Ki Karange Paaji
story: In his debut special, acclaimed comedian Sal Vulcano vividly recalls the fears he had throughout his adolescent life and how they simply have lingered much too long into adulthood. The special offers a charming perspective of Vulcano's hysterical real-life experiences with the lies about thunder, surprisingly menacing 80s song lyrics, and the war against moths that never quite happened. With animated storytelling and clever punchlines, this special showcases Vulcano's unique style and reinforces why he is a mainstay in the world of comedy.

name: 1350. Shri Swapankumarer Badami Hyenar Kobole
story: Trapped inside the elevator of a hotel casino complex, an elevator boy falls in love with his investor's girlfriend that forces him to choose between his love for her, or his dreams for a better future.

name: 1351. Moorane Krishnappa
story: In 2122 AD when world faces an imminent problem from a rogue nation, Indrani working for Indian Super Force (ISF) has to travel in time to past to find the solution for it. Story revolves around the emotional journey of Indrani.

name: 1352. shukrddosh
story: Two prisoners, Jarnail Singh and Tarsem Lal, escape from prison on the day of Baisakhi. However, their troubles increase when they learn that they were to be pardoned by the jail minister.

name: 1353. Apaixonada
story: A young man struggles with a personal health problem, and goes out of his way looking for a cure and save his love life in this hilarious romantic drama. A movie with clean, situational comedy, light hearted drama and good music.

name: 1354. Håkan Bråkan 2
story: 8-year-old Kolya is not like everyone else. The boy's mother, Tatyana, following the doctors, no longer believes that the congenital disease will recede and the child will one day become "normal." But her new acquaintance Yuri is determined to put Kolya on his feet with the help of his unique gymnastics system. And when during classes it accidentally turns out that the boy has a talent for music, learning to play the piano becomes another step on the path to recovery. Ahead of Kolya is a prestigious piano competition in China and a lot of obstacles, which the healing power of music and fatherly love will help him overcome.

name: 1355. The Diarrhea Brothers Save the Day
story: Two strangers stuck in Los Angeles for the night are forced to confront their fears and take control of their lives.

name: 1356. Masthu Shades Unnai Ra
story: Tristán is a frustrated writer who lives by writing inspirational phrases on sugar sachets. His routine life is turned upside down when he agrees to transport the frozen corpse of his troubled brother Simón from Asturias to Benidorm.

name: 1357. Life Hotel
story: Two years ago, Comedian Cliff Cash embraced #Vanlife and has been traveling across the country doing hundreds of shows across various venues. "The Long Road," pays a comedic homage to his journeys and the lifestyle he's chosen to live.

name: 1358. Hiçbir Sey Normal Degil
story: 17-year-old top high school student Li Jinjin accidentally returned to the teenage years of her underachiever mother Li Qingtong, where she met her scumbag father whom she had never met before and her deceased grandparents. With a sudden inspiration, she quickly integrated into her mother's circle of friends, tearing apart her scumbag and crazily matching up with Wu Zhixun. Determined to "let my father go and not my mother," she embarked on a hilarious journey of changing fathers.

name: 1359. Les cadeaux
story: A bloody thriller (sort of Agatha Christie does The Twilight Zone) morphs into its own "making of", a really talky one - a conversation about film, about fear, about fiction. The type of film where the less you know, the better.

name: 1360. Vozvrashchenie popugaya Keshi
story: This movie is made in Honor of everyone who chased a God given dream in their Life.

name: 1361. Twelve
story: Víctor, an actor by profession, has just run as a candidate for the presidency of Ecuador. With the help of Wellington he will go through different situations that will take him away from the goal.

name: 1362. Caindo na Real
story: Eric O'Bannon ventures on a road trip in an attempt to prove to everyone that he's still got it. With the help of a talented, yet troubled teen and an eccentric drifter, they maneuver through the paranormal, mixing lessons in life with hysterical outcomes.

name: 1363. Emma
story: Freewheeling distiller Terry wrangles his brother Tobin into one of his poorly planned schemes; a show focused on wine, whiskey and food. Tobin is frustrated when Terry shows up with a film crew comprised of eccentric personalities armed with dubious abilities. Meanwhile, Sly Fox, Tobin's biggest competitor for the coveted Golden World Wine Award is cleverly plotting to steal the prestigious award and break his multi year winning streak.

name: 1364. The Gesuidouz
story: David Zarco, una vez un ídolo de la música, se encuentra en el abismo de su carrera, ahogado en deudas y sin rumbo en su vida. Todo cambia cuando descubre que tiene una hija de diez años en Perú, fruto de un amor del pasado.

name: 1365. Boomerang
story: Four clueless misfits set out on a journey to discover just what it is women want...what ensues is a rocket-ride of laughter.

name: 1366. Guardian
story: Marco, who is in his twenties and a bit lost, helps out a friend by standing in for him at his place of work: an emergency center for lifts. At around 3 am, a young woman called him: trapped in a broken-down car, she was having an anxiety attack. Marco tried to reassure her on the phone, but as no technician was available to help, he decided to go and rescue her himself. Unfortunately, when he arrives, the young woman has vanished into thin air. And so begins his incredible quest to track down this enigmatic stranger in Paris on the night of Valentine's Day.

name: 1367. Genis Aile 4: Cevahir & Ulvi
story: In a peaceful battery goli, where everyone took an oath not to fight amongst themselves, chaos ensues as another Female hops into the scene.

name: 1368. Aaichya Gavat Marathit Bol
story: A smart young man stumbles upon stolen money, which draws him into a dangerous web of crime led by a ruthless gang leader. Together with unlikely allies, he faces exciting challenges to uncover the truth and fight for the homeland

name: 1369. Itutumba ka ng tatay ko
story: Desperate to win a high-stakes dessert contest, chef Ben unintentionally cooks up an imaginary friend to help him reinvent the meaning of delicious. But what happens when his ambition becomes a monster?

name: 1370. Motu Patlu & The Race to the Diamond Valley
story: A devastating breakup leaves a struggling music artist unable to complete his much-anticipated second album. Desperate for inspiration, he enlists the help of his loving best friend to embark on a mission to find the perfect muse - the love of his life - in this music-driven romantic comedy.

name: 1371. Kill the Children first
story: On the day of Gandhi Jayanti, when meat sale is prohibited nationwide, an 11-year-old girl goes on a quirky adventure in pursuit of a forbidden chicken curry.

name: 1372. Mahajatra
story: Frances is the queen of San Francisco, until she steps out of her marriage to date young women who resist her rule.

name: 1373. Love Game
story: Babette unexpectedly finds herself sharing her small Parisian apartment with Edo, a Congolese refugee. When an escaped lab mouse makes itself known, their lives are turned upside down as they try to navigate conflicting expectations.

name: 1374. BAM!
story: An 80-year-old grandmother has been bedridden for over a month and the doctors have no answer to the mystery of her illness, but there lurks an answer.

name: 1375. The Other, Gold
story: Mehmet, who left his village to become a doctor, returns to his village years later, but his mind is still on the city. They make a plan to return to the city with their childhood friend Sefer. Gülbahar, who is aware of the plans, reverses the actions of Mehmet and Sefer because she is secretly in love with Mehmet.

name: 1376. Anyone Else But Me
story: The year is 1981. Manyunya has long dreamed of attending a concert of her favorite band "Zemlyane", but she could not imagine what incredible events and unexpected acquaintances await her and friends on Red Square, in the circus on Tsvetnoy Boulevard and in the parks of the capital.

name: 1377. Pailam Pilaga
story: The Selatan's two-year wait for answers was finally worth it. Alma is back. But with many questions in Selatan's head.

name: 1378. Surge of Power: Where There's Smoke
story: Two feuding matriarchs engage in chaos and dysfunction during a family beach vacation in prolific Algerian director Merzak Allouache's chaotic family dramedy.

name: 1379. Art Work
story: Slavik, a carefree Sochi resident, learns of a grave illness. His only hope is a long-lost brother - famous singer Philipp Kirkorov. To meet him, Slavik hatches a daring plan to kidnap Kirkorov, leading to an incredible adventure.

name: 1380. Super Zindagi
story: Salem, a Saudi engineer, pretends to be an Italian expert to work at a big company, exploiting the foreigner's advantage.

name: 1381. Passagrana
story: A Midwestern girl new to New York accidentally stumbles into an acting school and becomes obsessed with an unhinged acting teacher believing he is the key to her landing on TV.

name: 1382. Suswagatam Khushamadeed
story: Cult musician Swamp Dogg and housemates Moogstar and Guitar Shorty have turned their suburban LA home into an artistic haven. They journey through the turbulent music business, forming a special friendship transcending eras.

name: 1383. Kanni
story: Two roommates with contrasting lifestyles, must cohabitate despite their differences. Omero's homosexuality fuels Pietro's homophobia, leading to conflicts. Over time, they learn to understand and appreciate each other beyond prejudice.

name: 1384. Gangs of Sukumara Kurup
story: Natale in famiglia. Tutto il precario equilibrio tra i parenti verrà messo a repentaglio da un'enigmatica richiesta da parte della capo-famiglia, che metterà in seria crisi il clima natalizio.

name: 1385. A Trip Elsewhere
story: An Iranian athlete will do anything to emigrate from Iran. He went to Hong Kong from Iran and got involved in many adventures.

name: 1386. Ingiliz Anahtari: Recep Usta
story: Anya is an exemplary housewife who devoted her life to her family and three children. Relatives are accustomed to the fact that their mother is always at home and takes care of them. Husband Sasha disappears at work and admires his successful boss. One day, offended by her husband's inappropriate prank, Anya decides to leave him with her children, find a job and live independently. It turns out she doesn't get everything right away. At this time, children dream of returning their former "kind" mother and, using a dating application, arrange a casting of grooms to find her another husband and a new dad for themselves.

name: 1387. Do I Shock U Like Lightning
story: In Las Vegas, a go-go dancer and a call girl are terrorized by a giant evil rabbit.

name: 1388. Una película barata
story: After his father's death, a young man spirals into insanity and childhood nightmares that bring his fears to life. The mind can be deadly, but toys can be killer.

name: 1389. Kunwarapur
story: Follows the Di Rienzo family. Seemingly perfect, the Di Rienzo family is destabilized by the sudden death of the father of the family, an exemplary man, an established professional and a point of reference for everyone.

name: 1390. Amor en toda la cara
story: Three morally questionable friends wreak havoc across Manhattan with their selfish schemes and deranged attempts to help each other, spiraling into consequences they absolutely deserve.

name: 1391. Raja 420
story: Pablo Escobar's illegitimate Jewish son in Miami, Pablito, Treks to Medellin to trace his ancestral roots and starts the kosher cartel.

name: 1392. Solos en la noche
story: A look into the world of adult film legend William Margold as he struggles for his industry

name: 1393. Heads or Fails
story: 10 inter-connected stories of LGBTQ+ people pursuing life and love in the modern world, from a young straight man yearning to "convert," to dating veterans navigating the world during the Covid pandemic.

name: 1394. O Clube das Mulheres de Negócios
story: In a whimsical adventure, Otto Van Walrus creates a mischievous RoboPuffin to outshine the real puffins. Led by Johnny Puff, the feathered friends train to defend their home. Join the fun as they battle wits and show the power of teamwork.

name: 1395. Paranormal Cuma
story: Los Mecánicos 2 continues the story of Linda and her "No Hay Liga" racing team. After saving her father's company, and having her own son with Luis, Linda begins to feel the weight of building her own legacy, outside of her father's shadow. At this point, all team members have grown in the sport of acceleration. However, everyone's world takes a turn when an illegitimate daughter of Don Pepe reappears in Linda's life claiming "her inheritance." To do this, the girl has hired Linda's old boyfriend as a pilot. The conflicts lead Los Mecánicos to represent Puerto Rico in a world competition where they will have to put everything they have built on the line.

name: 1396. Un día en Culiacán
story: NATASHA'S Dance tells the tragicomic love story of the unworldly Daantje and the Russian Natasha, a woman who is socially isolated and scarred by life. It is an impossible love between two seemingly incompatible characters coming from two completely different backgrounds. A lighthearted mosaic of events illustrates their fatal connection, their final 'homecoming' and the sense and senselessness of life.

name: 1397. Fallen Fruit
story: Forbidden love. Familial strife. Political intrigue. In Cymbeline, the final play from Shakespeare's First Folio, the playwright fuses romance, comedy and tragedy to create a unique fantasia brimming with mistaken identities and gender-swapping disguises. Cymbeline's daughter, Innogen, one of Shakespeare's most celebrated heroines, is thrust into the world of court politics and ruthless personal ambitions when she chooses a lover beneath her station. Deceived by the dastardly Iachimo, a worthy contender for the Bard's all-time greatest villain, Innogen must fight to protect her honour and agency.

name: 1398. Rock and Doris (try to) Write a Movie
story: Scientists use nanotechnology to shrink a shark, which is injected into a person to cure a rare blood disorder. When the shark does more harm than good, a team of adventurers enters the bloodstream to kill the smallest shark ever.

name: 1399. All's Fair in Love
story: Two different gangs try to kidnap the same person which unfolds a big conspiracy.

name: 1400. Zahradníkuv rok
story: A group of intelligent dinosaurs living peacefully on their island face turmoil when a madman captures them and seizes control. After escaping, they unite to reclaim their home.

name: 1401. Opportunity
story: A lefty lesbian couple and their lapdog accidentally beach their boat on a tiny remote Florida Key, crashing a right wing couple's campsite, and all must wait for the tide to come back in for them to get out.

name: 1402. East of Noon
story: Whilst serving a prison sentence for killing a gang boss, Liang gives birth to a boy who is put into welfare. 30 years later, Liang is released from prison, and the gang send blind Ah Gui to pose as Liang's blind son so he can kill her.

name: 1403. Noches de Sol
story: Nature Cat and his pals realize they've come to the end of their Nature Curiosity List. Meanwhile, Sir. Galahad gives himself the title of King and moves into a barren castle and steals pieces of nature to make his castle look more beautiful.

name: 1404. Melukis Harapan Di Langit India
story: Syarikat Ada Hantu Kami Setel will take care of the ghost entities in your home but when there are slaps involved, things comically aren't so easy nor straightforward.

name: 1405. Me Contro Te - Il film: Operazione Spie
story: Adam Roberts breaks his dad's rules of not playing his guitar and throwing parties after being left alone, leading to an unexpectedly negative week.

name: 1406. Foul Evil Deeds
story: The portrait of a Tunisian family living in France in the early 1990s when they discover that their landlord wishes to take back his apartment within a few months' time.

name: 1407. El Cas Àngelus. La fascinació de Dalí
story: A Californian backpacker becomes entangled in a polyamorous relationship with a gang of young actors who plot to kidnap the US Ambassador to Argentina.

name: 1408. Holy Irresistible
story: Two orphan girls' wish for parents remains unfulfilled. A troubled child joins them at the children's home. The director takes them on a farm visit to lift their spirits during the holidays, hoping to bring joy amidst their struggles.

name: 1409. Cici Anne
story: When his PI brother-in-law goes missing, soft-boiled sleuth Perry "Pears" Matthews is put on the case by his very pregnant sister and now will have to fill the gumshoes he never thought he had.

name: 1410. Muri & Ko
story: Adulterous L.A. Deejay Mr.C spins five tales of malice and deceit that will leave you all to die...Laughing.

name: 1411. Heavens: The Boy and His Robot
story: When Donald Trump and Rudy Giuliani land in prison, Trump sees it as his next big opportunity. With "Trump Bucks" and bold schemes, he aims to take over the prison in this hilarious, satirical take on power and corruption.

name: 1412. Hangama.Com
story: Two teenagers meet each other during a zombie apocalypse and has to get along to survive and along the way find a deeper meaning with their lives.

name: 1413. A Thousand Cuts
story: In "Full Custody," stand-up comedian Rodney Carter is gearing up for his highly anticipated comedy tour when life takes a wild turn. Just as he's about to hit the road, a woman unexpectedly shows up at his doorstep, claiming he's the father of her unruly son. With a DNA test confirming the shocking news, Rodney is thrown into a whirlwind of chaos, forced to confront his newfound responsibilities and the possibility of jail time if he doesn't step up. Deciding to embrace this unexpected chapter, Rodney reluctantly brings his son along on tour. Which results in a hilarious blend of stand-up comedy as he navigates the challenges of fatherhood and parenting on the road. From wild mishaps to laugh-out-loud moments, Rodney discovers that the real punchlines come from the unpredictable nature of family life. "Full Custody" is a heartwarming and comedic journey that explores the chaos of parenting while finding joy in the most unexpected situations.

name: 1414. On aurait dû aller en Grèce
story: Cheng Jialang and Wei Yifu are the contemporary poker twin stars, and they are about to have their first face-to-face confrontation. However, at this moment, Cheng Jialang accidentally transferred his poker talent to a small-time crook named Huang Xiaoqi, who had no previous experience. The two of them went through a wonderful journey and decided to join forces to challenge Wei Yifu.

name: 1415. Mike Epps: Ready to Sell Out
story: A young and ambitious guy from the village comes to the city to fulfill his dream and enter the Academy of the Ministry of Internal Affairs. His desire to become a policeman is known to everyone around him. However, in the area where his uncle lives, there is a criminal group that controls ruthless gangs, and when he enters the academy, he meets his love. Now he has to not only prepare for exams, but also enter into a confrontation with bandits in order to protect his loved ones and his future.

name: 1416. Demetri Martin: Demetri Deconstructed
story: I am a crocodile, a bloody crocodile. A wounded person who has lost his whole life and has nothing to lose - but still he wants to take big risks.

name: 1417. Mesru Gayrimesru
story: It's the summer of Barbie and Oppenheimer aka Barbenheimer, and The Egos take on blockbuster madness with a Top Gun parody. When streaming numbers plummet, they uncover the bizarre cult of Walt Disney.

name: 1418. Omar v bolshom kino
story: In peaceful Taigasville, the Puffins enjoy carefree days filled with arctic games, and even lazy Otto Von Walrus loves his picnics. But when a surprise snowstorm strikes, the Puffins must rally together to save their world. Otto included.

name: 1419. Deadpool Just Another Day
story: When incompatible sisters - a free-spirit wanderer and a neurotic bride-to-be - face their harbored resentment, family knots unravel as the wedding day approaches.

name: 1420. Mi Perfecto Ex
story: Anthology film featuring the early shorts of Monty Wolfe

name: 1421. Hope's Hollywood Christmas
story: In the year 1984, TV Journalist, Donna Detweiler, takes you on a journey with her documentary segment "Down and Out with Donna Detweiler." In episode 6 of season 4, she aims to uncover the lost history whereabouts of the English punk rock band, Sachwheel.

name: 1422. Bro
story: In the quaint heartland of rural India, Panchanan Sapui, a gifted yet impoverished polymath, resides in the benevolent Ramtanu Babu's household with his wife Padmavati and their son Bhootnath. Following Panchanan's untimely demise, Bhootnath inherits his father's humble rice warehouse and clandestine gambling den. As Bhootnath navigates the complexities of love, family, and fate, he finds himself entwined in a romantic affair with Gauri, Ramtanu Babu's lovely daughter. However, their love is threatened by Totla Totaram, the ambitious son of Ramtanu Babu's friend Kestcharan. In a serendipitous twist, Bhootnath's life takes a dramatic turn when, disguised as Lord Shiva, he encounters four hapless ghosts in the forest. Mistaking him for the divine Mahadev, the ghosts shower him with blessings, transforming his destiny. Upon awakening, Bhootnath discovers his dreams have miraculously materialized. As the story unfolds, Bhootnath's journey culminates in a joyous union with Gauri, restoring harmony.

name: 1423. The Drunken Prodigy
story: What should a husband do if his wife writes to him that she is with a friend, and now he is with this friend?

name: 1424. Son Sans
story: A love triangle unfolds between two men and a woman, exploring the intense and bittersweet emotions of their entanglement, set against the backdrop of Chiayi City's retro streets evoking old Japan.

name: 1425. King Blvd
story: In this film, when all 4 of Shrek's old nemesis come back from the dead and kill Fiona, he must find a way to bring Fiona back from the dead via magical contract, all with the help of Donkey, Puss, and some new faces.

name: 1426. Aumenta que é Rock'n'Roll
story: Two men come into the life of the young and pretty Marika Ábel: a man of progress, a calculating railway engineer, and a romantic, mysterious baron.

name: 1427. On fait quoi maintenant?
story: Udan, a young man who puts his life goals at a crossroads, between pursuing his idealism as a musician or living life realistically by working like other people in general.

name: 1428. Rush Hour
story: Henk Opperman, a psychologist coping with the emotional aftermath of losing his wife in a tragic car accident, struggles to connect with his son Renier, who masks his emotions behind anger and denial. During Nicolene's funeral, Henk confesses to leaking the Matric Math Paper to Barberton in 1990. An investigation leads to an ultimatum: retake the exam in Barberton or forfeit academic records. Henk and Renier reconcile as Renier tutors him, joined by Henk's eccentric father and Renier's friends. Tensions rise with Henk's classmates, culminating in a pivotal moment where Henk must choose between reconciling with his son and saving his career.

name: 1429. Christmas with the Pups 2: Pups Alone
story: Set in Kochi right before the pandemic, micro-celebrity and boy genius Gabriel finds himself in the midst of an ugly rumor as he deals with small people with big city ideas.

name: 1430. Die Chaosschwestern und Pinguin Paul
story: Metin and Hande got married after a long period of dating, but they divorced after a while. One day, the mother of the two surprises them and comes to their house. Since Hande's mother, Leman, has heart disease, Hande and Metin did not tell their families that they were divorced.

name: 1431. Kyllä isä osaa -elokuva
story: Juanita decides to abandon her family and go to a convent where, together with a group of extravagant nuns, she must discover the mysterious murder of a priest.

name: 1432. Christmas Overtime
story: Made up of three substantial yet uniquely identifiable Christmas tales, ADVENT sees numerous specific lives all caught up over the course of a magical December 24th.

name: 1433. The Stork
story: Before they can have sex, three couples must survive a night of unexpected and awkward adventures that force them to re-examine their views on love and intimacy.

name: 1434. Person of the Year
story: WHEN FEUDING SISTERS FIND THEMSELVES VYING FOR THE AFFECTIONS OF THE SAME 'RENT-A-BAE' BOYFRIEND DURING A CHAOTIC CHRISTMAS DINNER, THEY DISCOVER THAT THE REAL COMPETITION IS FOR THE BONDS OF FAMILY, LOVE, AND FORGIVENESS.

name: 1435. Sal Vulcano: Terrified
story: A story of six individuals stuck inside a grocery store at the height of the strongest storm.

name: 1436. Elevator
story: Three friends bond and their coming of age graph against a backdrop of kite-flying as a sports event.

name: 1437. Indrani: Epic-1 Dharam vs Karam
story: Ongoing anti-gang operation captures elusive gangster kingpin. Police force faces threats from money laundering syndicates. Old cases resurface, involving businessmen and officials. Risky investigation endangers cops' lives.

name: 1438. Ajab Gajab Dhamal
story: Two underachieving sons of a legendary football coach head to a remote island in Greece to coach the Salty Amazons, a struggling women's football team stuck for decades in a chaotic corrupt league - "The Prison League."

name: 1439. Pushpaka Vimanam
story: Romina, a controlling lawyer, wants her daughter's affection. She offers rent for a recovering alcoholic's dog in exchange for a fake boyfriend role. Unexpectedly, it might turn real.

name: 1440. Just a Minute
story: Jenny is a typical teen with a difficult home life. One night while sleeping she is transported to an empty void where she finds herself on trial, an angel and demon making cases for her soul.

name: 1441. Nenormalnyy
story: "Here She Comes" tells the story of Emma and Rene, two experiential sex coaches who lead America into the next sexual revolution, and the army of terrified spouses, religious fundamentalists, and misogynist loners that try to stop them.

name: 1442. Union Station
story: A spoiled Colombian man uses his wealth and connections to become president, but discovers that maintaining power requires more than just money and influence.

name: 1443. Lo carga el diablo
story: The journey of Anil, an obedient boy, is changed after an event and bond with a colleague alters his worldview.

name: 1444. Cliff Cash: The Long Road
story: From embracing his inner hater to the rigid rules of masculinity, the comic Brian Simpson goes full throttle during his stand-up routine live from The Comedy Mothership, in Austin, Texas.

name: 1445. Be My Friend
story: A teen rebel and a runaway bride meet up as strangers in Amsterdam and form an unlikely bond.

name: 1446. Ext. Masina. Noapte
story: A missing bride-to-be, a course for confused men, a couple in crisis, a Carnival monster, marmot hunters and a glacier in peril. Will the community of Excelsior be able to face up to its contradictions as everything falls apart?

name: 1447. Hollywood Dreams
story: Jay Banks, a successful news reporter blames women for his short comings of falling in and out of love. In order to aid his problem, Jay seeks the help of a magical edible that's supposed to change his perception on women. In doing so, Jay beings to understand that physical attraction is the least characteristic of a long lasting relationship.

name: 1448. Víctor Presidente
story: Javi is undocumented and on the verge of being deported, when he bumps into his estranged best friend Hunter, a boisterous bachelor yearning for connection. Together, they fight to keep Javi in the only country he's ever known.

name: 1449. Bye Bye Kitty
story: Influencers do anything and everything to become more famous, but what if they have to risk their lives for it?

name: 1450. Wine Thief
story: Malik brings uptight girlfriend to meet family for Christmas. They disapprove of her. He meets nurse Rain, realizes true love, and what he desires for holiday.

name: 1451. Amiche mai
story: A principal (Eric Roberts) has no choice but to let a fun but irresponsible teacher's assistant teach summer school. He has to get his act together to get the kids to pass and to win the heart of the teacher next door.

name: 1452. Ari-cassamortari
story: In order to save her father's deteriorating business, Yasemin is forced to marry Mehmet, the son of a farm owner family who lives a rich but modest life. She persuades him to marry with various tricks, and as soon as she gets what she wants, she abandons Mehmet, whom she tries to break up with, and runs away.

name: 1453. Papá Por Sorpresa
story: A regular guy, overwhelmed by life's challenges, pleads for divine intervention. Unexpectedly granted the ability to hear people's thoughts, he's caught in a moral dilemma. Can this newfound power bring solace or turmoil?

name: 1454. Women Want Everything!
story: The brownie escapes from the captivity of Baba Yaga in her magical world, and ends up in the apartment of the girl Natasha and her parents. Kuzya needs to find his magic chest that grants wishes. Both Natasha and the local grumpy brownie Nafanya help him in this. It turns out that Kuzya himself gave the chest to Andrey, Natasha's dad, many years ago. It would seem that the goal is already close, but in search of both Kuzya and the chest, Baba Yaga entered our world, and she has her own insidious plans.

name: 1455. Elle & lui & le reste du monde
story: Un grupo de comediantes que está atravesando una crisis laboral decide asistir a una misteriosa fiesta, la cual se sale de control, pues termina en un asesinato. ¿Será que ellos son culpables?

name: 1456. Female 4
story: A selfish narcissist and his cash-strapped best friend hire a corrupt notary to swindle his estranged brother. After the notary dies in a freak accident, their elaborate scheme goes off the rails.

name: 1457. Blindgänger
story: A decade since their last escapades, the beloved idiots face contemporary challenges with the trademark irreverent humor fans cherish.

name: 1458. The Max Gang
story: Thakur, a passionate filmmaker, had one dream: to create that could capture the spice, drama, and humor of Indian life. Inspired by the classic Indian dish Cholay. After his audition he finally found his casts Veeru,Basanti,Jay and Gabbar.

name: 1459. All the Wrong Ingredients
story: Neath owes a lot of money to her village. Dao has fallen in love with her and helped her pay off her debt, but Neath still does not love him back. Because Dao is a womanizer. Dao tries many ways to make her fall in love with him.

name: 1460. La scommessa - Una notte in corsia
story: Diane and Fox love to work. Unfortunately, they live in a polarized world where having a job is illegal.

name: 1461. Lovers and Friends
story: This film is exploring the lives of a filmmaker and his crew.

name: 1462. Naale Rajaa Koli Majaa
story: Romantic Bionico struggles to find a job and home to provide for fiancée La Flaca after rehab. He tries to quit drugs with help from his partner Calvita.

name: 1463. Il complottista
story: In Taigasville, the wicked walrus Otto steals an ancient spellbook from the local shaman. Little does he know, this mischief opens a whimsical portal to a dream-filled dimension. Now, Otto must face insane challenges to set things right.

name: 1464. Sneaking Around
story: Sanjana's feelings for her childhood crush Ajay reawaken through virtual interactions. They bond over phone calls during lockdown, forming a connection without traditional labels, but face hurdles in recognizing their emotions.

name: 1465. Maoussi
story: Dan and Lisa live in the same city and suffer from the same predicament: not being able to sleep since being dumped. As they navigate the perilous world of modern dating they find joy, pain, confusion, rejection, sex...but never a good night's sleep.

name: 1466. Saka Perawan
story: A time traveler accidentally stuck in the modern era needs help returning to the year 2005 to save the year 2005 from weapons of mass destruction.

name: 1467. Gidersen Gitme
story: When a rookie journalist is thrown into the deep end with the job of covering the death of a high-profile figure, she finds herself in a quirky predicament. Her mission? To crash at the home of the deceased's youngest daughter, who's supposed to spill all the juicy details. But what starts as a straightforward assignment quickly spirals into a hilarious escapade filled with unexpected guests-some she'd rather avoid and others she's been eagerly anticipating. In just a few wild hours, this comical rollercoaster ride transforms her outlook on life in the most unexpected ways.

name: 1468. Manyunya. Priklyucheniya v Moskve
story: Fresh out of school, Félix and Vincent are two young broken arms from the Atlantic coast who are struggling to find their place in the world of work... and in life in general. The two friends decide to clandestinely transform a small neighborhood grocery store into a night-time business during the holidays. With the help of a team of specialists recruited for the occasion, they will keep the shop running, until the real owner of the supermarket and the police start to sniff out the bad move.

name: 1469. Ayo Balikan
story: João is about to visit the Universal parks in Orlando, but his boss asks him to hand over her son, Carlos Alberto, to his father in the United States. When the father doesn't show up, João and Carlos Alberto are forced to stay together.

name: 1470. Front Row
story: In North Bengal there was a village where crime rate was very high. That time lakhi Daroga posted their as a police man. And his nephew Ayan. Ayan was a brat. But after meeting with Labanya he became change into a different man.

name: 1471. Bratya
story: What love does to us: At the funeral of his best mate 19-year old Anton promises to fall in love, once and for real. But it doesn't seem to be all that easy - The story of his most important dates evolves into Anton's life story.

name: 1472. Chapter 51
story: Alex is a student in middle school and has a crush on a girl in his school. He has been trying to impress her by being kind and helpful, but unfortunately, a bully in the school has been making his life miserable. The bully constantly teases and taunts Alex, making it difficult for him to focus on his studies and personal life. One day, Alex decides to confront the bully and stand up for himself. He is determined to prove that he is not someone to be messed with and that he won't tolerate being bullied anymore until a fight is settled.

name: 1473. Il Signore
story: All Nour wants is a damn cigarette.

name: 1474. Intention
story: Dasha, at first glance, does not have a life, but a fairy tale. She holds a high position in the Ministry of Culture, and the young man who bought an apartment for their future family is in love with her. But in reality, not everything is going smoothly at work, the new apartment overlooks a vacant lot, and the lover is more interested in his mother's opinion. Dasha decides to escape - on a business trip around the Perm region. The young bar owner Sergey becomes her unexpected companion. Now people who are strangers to each other will have to travel through Perm cities and villages, meeting people who are alien to the ambitions and bustle of the metropolis.

name: 1475. Swamp Dogg Gets His Pool Painted
story: In this second and unneeded installment, the Delusion is so Strong that Brandon and Elliot Find themselves in a Real Narrative Film as Two Washed-up Vice Cops Resurrected from Retirement and Assigned to take down a Dangerous group of Criminals Dealing Drugs, Distributing Guns and Trafficking Women around the Gull Lake area.

name: 1476. Amici per caso
story: The peaceful life of a Moravian village is disturbed by a strange phenomenon. Amateur astronomer Blazej is convinced that there is a visitor from space. But no one believes him. But why does the neighbor Franta suddenly behave strangely?

name: 1477. Natale in famiglia
story: Two struggling real estate agents unexpectedly acquire an exclusive mansion but discover a dead body, leading them on a chaotic journey to secure a life-changing deal while evading trouble.

name: 1478. Hawaii
story: José, an educated farmer, cherishes his idyllic hillside village where he lives with family and beloved Ancy, surrounded by dear friends and community warmth.

name: 1479. Semeynyy perepolokh
story: A young videographer finds herself drawn into the orbit of Hadrian Burns, a fledgling UFO cultist, and his gang of lost boys.

name: 1480. Easter Evil
story: In 1969, a Mexican town harbors a secret about Neil Armstrong's birthplace. A journalist tries to uncover the truth and gain fame by convincing the residents to confirm the rumor that "El Güero" Armstrong was born there.

name: 1481. Teddiscare
story: The greatest Pickleball players in the world are invited to a winner take all tournament with deadly consequences.

name: 1482. Succede anche nelle migliori famiglie
story: Nee Dhaarey Nee Katha explores the theme of perseverance, through the lens of music. The film moves through seemingly lighthearted instances and conversations in engaging with the message of pursuing what makes one fulfilled.

name: 1483. 3 Schmucks
story: A filmmaker learns about his past life, in which he attempted to make the first ever Kannada movie.

name: 1484. Don't F with Pablo
story: A social media influencer faces allegations of rape and human trafficking in Romania. Experts in body language and forensics analyze his responses during questioning.

name: 1485. Sleaze Please: The World of Bill Margold
story: Seventeen-year-old Mati stares down a rabbit hole of drugs, sex, and self-delusion when she's taken hostage in a drug dealer's apartment full of desperate people who show her what she could become.

name: 1486. Coffee House Chronicles: The Final Movie
story: A young couple, Ryan and Michelle, move in together in Spring of 2020. Follows a year of their lives during the COVID-19 pandemic.

name: 1487. Robo Puffin
story: Ralph, a mourning detective, discovers an unwelcome lump and an equally unwelcome partner, Xavier. The investigator contends with Xavier's exuberance as they navigate a partnership between unlikely cases, themselves and a lump.

name: 1488. Los Mecánicos 2
story: The Sweet Life: A Hockey World Champion and lover of beautiful women and fast cars must endure an unexpected life obstacle. He doesn't want to disappoint his new friends and his family, whose existence he had no clue about. Vladimir Polivka in a new comedy from the makers of WOMEN ON THE RUN. Rosta Beran, a hockey player on the Czech national ice hockey team, is a cool guy. He lives in a luxury apartment, has a fast car and many young lovers that he picks using the motto "nothing above thirty". Money and the title of world champion make him feel like he's superior to everyone else, untouchable. However, nothing lasts forever... After unexpectedly collapsing in bed with a beautiful blonde, life draws a thick ECG line and ends his carefree days. His heart transplantation process is led by strict Doctor Magda (Petra Hrebickova), who he once spent a night with and never talked to since. The debts from his old life of extravagance rid him of all the money he had, and the only thing that Rosta is left with is the World Champion medal that his former manager and friend Rosta (Vojtech Kotek) saves for him. Rosta has to find it in him to start again with optimism, life energy, and courage. He's aided by Jindrich (Jan Cina), a serious and responsible guy raising a six-year-old daughter. He's got a heart of gold, and even though he starts out hating Rosta, they soon become best friends. Rosta, surprised, finds that the life of normal people can be as beautiful and one-of-a-kind as loving the right woman above thirty.

name: 1489. De Dans van Natasja
story: Yana lives in northern town, works at the post office, collects stamps and waits for her father from the sea, but she doesn't even hope for his coming home. One day sailor Petr comes to the post office, and it changes Yana's life.

name: 1490. Cymbeline
story: A panel of the sharpest comedians in the world today scorch each other with jokes and jabs that shouldn't be available for public consumption. Things are about to get heated.

name: 1491. Nanoshark
story: It is a heartwarming and humorous tale that showcases the beauty of cross-cultural relationships, the power of love, and the ability to overcome any obstacle in the pursuit of happiness.

name: 1492. Paarijathaparvam
story: Her name is Barbarian, your favorite doll from childhood. She lives in Los Angeles now-Skid Row, to be exact.

name: 1493. The Yoshi Movie
