story: Venu's well draws crowds in a parched area. His daughter Kingini loses her earrings in it, igniting conflicts that test relationships. A simple incident exposes underlying tensions.

name: 1494. Mud Key
story: Ace, the perfect son of the influential Mendoza family, falls for Gio, a gay porn star and sex worker. Despite seeing themselves as a match, Angelica, the family's uptight matriarch, disapproves of their relationship.

name: 1495. Second Life
story: Rudra Patil an architect is bewildered when he gets a match on a dating app but is uncertain about the legitimacy of the profile, but somehow, he meets his tragic destiny in the end.

name: 1496. Nature Cat's Nature Movie Special Extraordinaire
story: Kie, facing tragedies, prays at a shrine, discovering her family faces karma from her gangster ancestor. She meets gang members, including her great grandfather, Khung, to prevent misfortune.

name: 1497. Pui Pui Molcar the Movie: Molmax
story: Charle travels to India, Pakistan, Somalia, Middle East, North Africa, speaking local languages. Initially light-hearted, it takes a somber turn as he reveals his mission's purpose, impacting all.

name: 1498. Siapa Buka Lampu?
story: Sometime Before Yesterday. Or After Tomorrow. Somewhere Out In The Yonder. There Was This Guy.

name: 1499. Broken Strings
story: Two American secret agents must work together to infiltrate a suburban Christmas party, stop an exchange between undercover Soviet agents, and try not to kill each other in the process.

name: 1500. Reine Mère
story: Taxi driver Zhang Beijing was devastated at his son's wedding, and met single mother Li Xiaoqin. By chance, he became an influencer, and his sudden fame unexpectedly allowed him to gain everything he wanted.

name: 1501. Underground Orange
story: A social media influencer rises to the cusp of stardom only to be thrown into a fight for her life and the lives of those closest to her.

name: 1502. Parents for Christmas
story: Those Chinese four-character proverbs in our daily lives, and express Chinese people's compromise while facing problems. Would this "Lai dou lai le" (meaning: now that we've here) attitude solve problems, or drag us into further abyss?

name: 1503. Koparan Kardesler
story: Simone's perfect life unravels after her boyfriend cheats. She loses credibility but her friends convince her to embark on a 'ho phase', hilariously navigating the dating world to find a new Christmas romance.

name: 1504. Pears
story: Three reckless Kazakhstani men on a trip to America experience an emergency landing in Nigeria, which sets off series of misadventures that test their life ideals, leading to profound personal lessons.

name: 1505. Pulp Modern: Die Laughing
story: After more than 10 years apart, two sisters meet again and set off on a journey through the interior of the state of Minas Gerais in search of the mythical Saideira cachaça, the legacy of their grandfather.

name: 1506. Prisoner Trump: The Don of Cell Block B
story: Entrepreneur Micha returns to his hometown with a brilliant idea: He wants to convert his parents' estate into a wellness oasis. But the villagers are disillusioned by the economical crisis and hesitate to support his plans.

name: 1507. Se upp för zombies!
story: The teacher's daughter dreams of giving her mother an unusual gift for the New Year and making her happy. At a custom gift agency, she chooses the most expensive one - dinner with a star. But it was difficult to guess what kind of fee we were talking about, and now she and her friends have several months to earn this money. Musician friends help her with this. By coincidence, the star is my mother's unrequited high school love, and New Year's dinner with the star will take place against all odds.

name: 1508. Full Custody
story: Get ready for a hilarious and cringe-worthy twist on the zombie genre. Follow Alex and Ember as they stumble through the ups and downs of their new afterlife, packed with laughs, shocks, and unforgettable moments, love can be a killer!"

name: 1509. Po ke wang zhe
story: "Down Town" is an action comedy that follows the stories of T-Mo - the hustler, Hunny - the prostitute, and Jerry - the junkie, over the course of 24 hours in the criminal underbelly of Downtown Los Angeles.

name: 1510. Timuchin
story: A group plans a bachelor party, inviting strippers who demand a large sum. The party goes haywire with an unexpected attendee. Hilarious mishaps, violence, and twists ensue as the situation spirals out of control, derailing their plans.

name: 1511. Alligator Blood
story: In the style of Neil Simon and the feel of "The Big Chill," two washed-up B movie producers coerce a young, naïve screenwriter into helping them convince a "money guy" to invest in a picture based on the writer's script. The three hopefuls and their families' caravan up North to an enchanting bed and breakfast where they all anxiously await the arrival of the man with the money - the man who will supposedly make all their dreams come true. This compelling story is laced with fears, tears, laughs and insights; while delivering a surprise, yet very happy ending. Just the way Walt Disney would have liked it.

name: 1512. Barbenheimer and the Cult of Walt Disney
story: In a small village, a young man with an unrelenting passion for cinema teams up with an ambitious filmmaker, defying all odds to prove their talent and chase their dreams in the world of movies.

name: 1513. The Puffins: Arctic Games
story: Revolves around the lives of two families, where a mouse creates infinite chaos.

name: 1514. A Tuesday Wedding
story: A comedy with an overlap into the issue of fake news.

name: 1515. Fragments of Us
story: A los 35 años, Bobby parece tenerlo todo, excepto por un pequeño defecto: aún vive con su madre y no tiene la menor intención de cambiar.

name: 1516. Love Live! Nijigasaki High School Idol Club Final Chapter Part 1
story: Majka and Agata have as much in common as they divide. They are both over fifty, going through menopause and do not believe that anything in their lives will change for the better. One lives on the Baltic Sea, the other in the Tatra Mountains. One runs a confectionery shop, the other is a successful interior designer. One is a widow, the other is just left by her partner for a younger woman. One devotes herself to her children and grandchildren, completely forgetting about herself, the other has no family and cares about her spiritual development. One day, the friends meet at the funeral of a high school friend. Agata encourages Majka to spontaneously go to the mountains, and she takes her place. The unexpected role reversal brings a number of complications, funny twists and challenges that the women will have to face. Will they be able to overcome their habits, prejudices and fears? Will they find the courage to open up to love and start a new chapter in their lives? Is it really never too late for anything?

name: 1517. The Ghost House
story: Within Hong Kong's bustling cityscape, vignettes intertwine the lives of its inhabitants, bound by tea, cigarettes, and broken lighters, as they grapple with life's myriad facets, and themselves.

name: 1518. Down and Out with Donna Detweiler: The Legacy of Sachwheel
story: Derrick's lifelong friend marries, making Derrick vow to never marry. One day, he falls asleep and finds himself trapped in an unexpected situation that feels alarmingly real, involving marriage against his will.

name: 1519. Bhooter Pallay Bhootnath
story: The romantic reunion of Ben Santhanaraj and Suzanne Hopper is thwarted when Suzanne's boss asks her to work during their holiday road trip.

name: 1520. Pravo na levo
story: Pietro was an child prodigy in the showbiz. Now that he is almost 30, he is no longer either a child or a prodigy. Pietro is now spending his life taping for auditions he never gets. He teaches theatre at a church close to his house and, following his precarious finances, he lives in a modest flat owned by the diocese for which he doesn't pay much. He shares the flat with Nicolas, an hospital nurse, divorced, a wife and a son to take care of, a chaotic and careless personality. That's why when they receive an eviction note, Nicolas avoids the issue by stating that Pietro has cancer. It is the start of an awful lie. Pietro lives the issue helplessly but then, when he is about to tell the truth, he meets Claudia, a terminally ill girl. Even if weakened by her disease, Claudia gushes life from every pore on her body. She is extroverted, lovely, deep, smart, happy to the extent that Pietro is completely dazzled by her and cannot find the courage to speak his truth. The lie made up by Nicolas becomes the unbreakable bond between Claudia and Pietro. A double link that unites them by making them completely different than all the others. A bond that Pietro, even if tormented by guilt, cannot give up.

name: 1521. Ana We Ibn Khalty
story: When a hard working soviet worker realises how disappointing his pension is, he starts talking to the Secretary General of the USSR and hanging out with the top communist figures from all over the world.

name: 1522. Ame no naka no yokujô
story: A dark comedy about a rich family getting their just desserts.

name: 1523. Tyrus: Here and Now
story: Alessandro, an aspiring serial killer, hires a film crew to make a documentary about his life and his murderous circle of "friends"

name: 1524. Shrek 5: The Contract - A Fan Made Film
story: A brilliant tech entrepreneur, on the verge of making his fortune, returns home for the first time in years and faces his painful past.

name: 1525. Majdnem menyasszony
story: An alcoholic decides to quit alcohol only to find out that drinking will help him avoid a life-threatening issue.

name: 1526. Up the Catalogue
story: After having an otherworldly vision, a spirited Indian-American boy convinces himself he's the reincarnation of Krishna. Turns out he's just gay.

name: 1527. Mendung tanpo udan
story: Two shady best friends will do anything to "come up" - no scams are off limits with these two. Watch as Kevin and Lovell try to scam their way to money and success.

name: 1528. Som van Twee
story: Joel gathers his friends at a remote cabin to celebrate the completion of his latest feature film in his 12 features project.

name: 1529. Watusi Zombie!
story: An existential mockumentary of Satan trying to adapt again to a modern society that he may not fit into.

name: 1530. Biz Ayrilamayiz
story: Frustrated by the injustice and hypocrisy of society, few good hearted thieves try to pull the heist of a lifetime to humorous ends.

name: 1531. La reina del convento
story: "Just Nesh: Self Served" is the Specialist Special to ever Special. You'll follow the uproarious adventures of Just Nesh, a Chicago comic with dreams as big as her laughter. Armed with a smartphone and unfiltered humor, she embarks on a unique quest to create the ultimate selfie comedy movie. From spontaneous home setups to comic relief in the car, and side-splitting moments on stages nationwide, Nesh brings the audience along for an unforgettable ride.

name: 1532. Advent
story: People will hold your past up against you.

name: 1533. B4S: Truoc Gio Yeu
story: A family inadvertently witnesses a murder and devises a scheme to profit from it, sparking a chain of comical mishaps.

name: 1534. Christmas Bae
story: After impulsively moving in with his girlfriend, André finds out that Dalene is still friends with all of her ex-boyfriends. Intimidated, André tries to befriend them and discovers that Dalene's relationships follow an exact pattern.

name: 1535. Pushcart Tales
story: Ali, an amateur actor, gets caught up in a bizarre situation after he posts a compromising selfie on social media. The photo captures Sam with his mistress, Ibtissam. To protect Sam, Ali is asked to pose as her lover. Tricked into believing he is auditioning for a film, Ali agrees to take on the "role." But Ibtissam is kidnapped by a gang, plunging Ali and his friends into a dangerous adventure.

name: 1536. Patang
story: Jesus Christ returns, and for his second coming, he's running for congress. Jesus finds a tough time learning what it means to be a Republican politician in the 21st century. But with guidance by his conniving campaign manager and a less-than-stellar campaign staff, Jesus picks it up quick enough. And we watch him become lost in it.

name: 1537. Walk the Line
story: Pop singer Camille Trust's bittersweet struggle in New York's cutthroat music scene navigating sleazy producers, vengeful Swifties, heartbreak and self-sabotage. Raw, messy and loosely based on true events.

name: 1538. Salty Amazons
story: When Alain Brel is supposed to play, his fate mixes with that of the artist. This encounter brings him closer to his daughter and turns his life upside down

name: 1539. Home & Away
story: A couple opts for a low-key cohabitation, keeping it under wraps from their families. What happens when the traditional parents come to know? Enjoy this comedy about love, family and everyday life.

name: 1540. Perra Vida
story: Tamara is the owner of a successful bakery and creator of spectacular sweets. About to marry Beto, she is determined to make her dream come true: to wear the same wedding dress as her mother, Verônica, on her big day.

name: 1541. Paradise
story: When people in their hometown begin dying on the anniversary of an accused witch's execution, a depressed journalist and his teenage sister set out to uncover the truth behind a local legend.

name: 1542. Here She Comes
story: A feisty but down-on-his-luck thug starts rebelling in unexpected ways after his emotionally manipulative boss keeps him trapped and working in a mechanic shop for four years.

name: 1543. Juanpis González: The People's President
story: Piotrus - together with his wife, mother-in-law and Leopold - moves to a new home: a historic manor house. And Marlenka decides to find a suitable ancestor for her family who will fit into the elegant residence... Agnieszka, in turn, is pursuing a career at the university, but right after defending her doctorate, she suddenly discovers that she is pregnant. And when little Kuba is born... problems begin. Piotrus accompanies his sister during childbirth and begins to dream of a child himself - to Marlenka's horror. Marcin, a new father, panics and suddenly disappears. And in addition, the mysterious Kamila appears in Brzózki - a very pregnant girl who is looking for Zawada.

name: 1544. Mirg
story: Chrissy is a teen who spends all her time online. After being pushed to the brink by both of her parents, she steals her mom's car and runs away to pick up her internet boyfriend.

name: 1545. Brian Simpson: Live from the Mothership
story: In the stunning mountains of Atok, Benguet, a wealthy, carefree man and a young woman haunted by her past accidentally cross paths. Together, they discover solace in each other's company until the truth catches up and confronts them.

name: 1546. Day Trippers
story: It's summertime in Memphis, Tennessee and the annual Hot Wing Contest is about to roll through. Cordell has his sights set on the crown this year, with the support of his partner Dwayne and friends, Isom and Big Charles. Together, they are The New Wing Order, and they're serving wings worthy of 'kangs'. Cordell's culinary crew are getting ready to fire up his new mouth-watering 'finna-be first-place' recipe, when the arrival of an unexpected guest throws some extra heat up in the kitchen on prep night. As the temperature rises and the sauce boils over, it seems a first-place trophy and a grand cash prize aren't the only things Cordell risks losing. Can he take the heat, or will he have to get out the kitchen?

name: 1547. Espèce menacée
story: Charismatic burglar Maksim gets into trouble after owing money to dangerous bandits. During the next robbery, he witnesses a desperate act committed by the apartment owner Eva, who has unexpectedly returned: she tries to burn everything that reminds her of her traitorous boyfriend, and in addition, commit suicide. Maksim decides to stop Eva and save himself from even bigger problems.

name: 1548. Diminishing Value of Love
story: Brothers, Ramses and Ahmos, cursed since the days of the Pharaohs, are the last two vampires in Egypt. After stumbling upon an ancient secret, they embark on a comedic journey of "self-reflection", brotherly love, and survival in the year 2023

name: 1549. The Compatriots
story: The life of foreman Ivan Plotnikov has been going downhill for a long time because of his invincible habit of enduring everything. But, by chance finding himself at the Russian bathhouse championship, he learns that this is not a curse at all, but a great talent. Now he will have to fully develop his ability to endure in order to finally believe in himself, regain the respect of his loved ones and compete for the solid cash prize that he so desperately needs.

name: 1550. Influenza
story: Misdiagnosed with a terminal illness, a computer nerd dates his hospice worker, while suspecting someone is out to get him.

name: 1551. Rain for Christmas
story: Single mom Kate is contemplating leaving the floundering small-town family business behind for the big-city life when she finds romance in an unlikely source in her hometown.

name: 1552. Bad Substitute
story: A fictional autobiography about an insecure, awkward and lonely actor who goes on an unwitting journey of self-love in the midst of an eating disorder relapse.

name: 1553. 30 anni di meno
story: Youn'G is a coming-of-age dramedy about a teenage boy who, with the help of his close friends, fights for his true love while at the same time discovering his cool neighborhood mentor is his father. Youn'G finds his way through the craziness of life, friendships, and family...all in three days.

name: 1554. Çiftligimin Hanimi
story: Ryan, a reclusive pothead, agrees to get highly functioning autistic classmate Edward high in exchange for homework answers but soon realizes he's in for more than he bargained for when Edward makes advances at friendship. Rosetta Stoned is a micro budget passion project that was filmed entirely in Ann Arbor, MI, on a budget of roughly $30,000. If rated by the MPAA, Rosetta Stoned would be rated R for language, drug use, sexual content, and partial nudity.

name: 1555. Problem Toh Hai
story: In the comedic chaos of "Chor Chor," pickpockets unwittingly exchange a stolen statue for a meal, leading to a hilarious alliance with rival thieves in pursuit of treasure.

name: 1556. Domovyonok Kuzya
story: KCHILL and Bella are in a tight situation. She ask him to get a Powerball ticket with the last of their money. Only problem is he switched the numbers around so what will happen next.

name: 1557. Los De La Culpa
story: Struggling through the loneliness of lockdown, a group of theatre artists seek ways to find community and experience their craft via that most isolating of locations--the internet.

name: 1558. Con Job
story: Thirty years after a horrifying event forced its closure, a group of camp counselors is tasked with re-opening Camp Sack-In under new ownership. Little do they know that dark secrets from the past linger in the woods. The campers are forced to fight for their lives as an axe-wielding Woodsman stalks them and exacts brutal revenge on anyone unlucky enough to cross his path.

name: 1559. I soliti idioti 3: Il ritorno
story: Noah is a 17-year-old boy who goes to Luna's house to help her with the philosophy exam she has the next day. Luna is a girl who questions everything and prefers to spend the night thinking about her boyfriend rather than studying for the exam. Plato's dialectic intertwines with their experiences on a night where they will end up leaving the cave to discover the true meaning hidden behind Platonic Love.

name: 1560. Cholay
story: Fleeing her ex-con ex-lover who is seeking a secret flash drive, a woman and her son move to a new city and find allies who teach the boy kung fu.

name: 1561. Neath's Love Story
story: A young German, Werner Müller, turns out to be a volunteer in the neurological department of an ordinary St. Petersburg hospital. A foreigner, overwhelmed by the impulse to help all the sick and needy, has a long and eventful day ahead of him. Every now and then, finding himself in comical situations and making his way through misunderstandings, the volunteer discovers all the facets of the Russian national character.

name: 1562. Love and Work
story: The small town of Uranus has been invaded. Two best friend and fudge packing employees at the Uranus Fudge Factory now must save Uranus and stop an evil hive-mind Alien slug named Zamik before he "ass-similates" all of Uranus.

name: 1563. Tan-Ti-Ana
story: After savaging a reclusive Director's new film, a disenchanted Film Critic is surprised to find himself invited to dinner with them, where their match of wits soon turns into something far more sinister.

name: 1564. Bionico's Bachata
story: When the temple near Teng's hometown had problems, Teng had to leave the peace that he used to have as a safe zone while in Tibet to come back and solve the problem. But when he returned, he had to face a universal problem in the religious world.

name: 1565. The Puffins & the Magic Portal
story: A couple's arranged marriage faces uncertainty when a nationwide lockdown occurs. They connect through video calls, getting to know each other, but fate has surprises in store.

name: 1566. Konjam Pesinaal Yenna
story: A highly commercially successful rock band mysteriously disbanded before their first concert. 30 years later, they have a second chance.

name: 1567. I Can't Sleep Without You
story: A film-maker from Scotland travels to California to shoot a true crime documentary. However, it seems that the real crime, is the film that they are making.

name: 1568. Back to 2005
story: The lives of Kartheek and Sombabu, who face adversity and redemption.

name: 1569. Goodbye Hamdi
story: A hot dog-loving, Hatfield, Pennsylvania cryptid has been rediscovered and people need you to know about it. Join Hatfield residents, Crick Foot lovers, and scientists as they try to track him down.

name: 1570. Presque légal
story: Sabonis, Eduardo and Modesto get in troubles again when the wife of the Portuguese criminal lord they helped to arrest appears claiming to recover the lost money when he was arrested.

name: 1571. Two's a Crowd in Orlando
story: In Japan, Rokurokubi are known to be like Vampires. They're known to be dangerous Yokai for committing horrible deeds. Except for one. Asumi Mayako -- Born a Rokurokubi, now lives a normal life with Karita Dere. Twelve years have passed since Asumi was found in the trash can, and things have been a little complex since Karita and her family decided to adopt Asumi. Asumi still feels worried about what would happen If people found out she's a rokurokubi. However, things get complicated when Asumi's mother, Khayme Mayako is slowly crawling back into her life. Not just that - Asumi's worries and nightmares become a reality as a reunion between Yokai and humans has begun. Experience an animated trip starring a Rokurokubi with a heart of gold.

name: 1572. Daroga Mamur Kirti
story: A failed product copywriter with an alcohol dependency crosses paths with a mysterious stranger on a personal mission and together they embark on an unforgettable adventure across the neon-lit Shanghai.

name: 1573. Einmal richtig
story: A stray dog was born on the street and learned to survive there: steal sausages, warm himself in doorways and make friends. One day, while fleeing from an evil saleswoman, he falls into a deep hole and cannot get out. He is saved by Mikhail, an elderly and lonely man with whom his family does not really want to communicate. He saves him and gives him a name - Styopka. It would seem that Mikhail and Styopka found each other so as not to be lonely, but when Mikhail brings the dog home, he feels bad. And now Styopka has very little time to call for help and save the life of his owner. But it is very difficult to do this, because none of the people understands it. Or is this not entirely true?

name: 1574. Alex and Mia's Awesome Movie!!
story: A spooky comedy about a couple who venture to a cabin in the woods to find a page torn from an evil book. Once they arrive, things get weird. They must unfold the mystery, defeat the occultist, his talking pumpkin, and a malevolent spirit.

name: 1575. Two Sisters
story: Orthodox father and progressive mother travel to Dubai to visit their son.

name: 1576. Vtroyom
story: A young man pursues a relationship with an independent street vendor. Despite their differences, he tries various ways to convince her to marry him.

name: 1577. Gull Lake Vice II: The Delusion Continues
story: In the dark depths of the net, Bernadette teams up with the enigmatic influencer duo Kitty and Peter to orchestrate the demise of student Lotte - a live stream meant to leave the internet buzzing.

name: 1578. Franta mimozemstan
story: Four strangers brought together by chance in a police station. They believe that money is the ultimate solution to all their problems. When desperation and determination collide, they make a reckless decision to kidnap an MLA's daughter.

name: 1579. Real Estate Sisters
story: Set in 1349, during the devastation of the plague; two long lost brothers seek out a forgotten doctrine that declares the last surviving member of their land, lord.

name: 1580. Swargathile Katturumbu
story: Two stoners become powerlifters to win cash for weed and rent.

name: 1581. Church of the Flying Saucer
story: The protagonist, Sasanami Unmei, transfers to Nagumohara Junior High School in Nagasaki in search of a soccer-free environment, wishing that soccer would disappear. Meanwhile, Endou Haru, who has demonstrated his natural talent and reigns at the top of his generation, also has complicated feelings about soccer. The unexpected encounter between these two opens the door to new heroes.

name: 1582. Un mexicano en la luna
story: Maks steals a collectible Cadillac from a local authoritative businessman German Eduardovich. Gus is trying to help his friend, even though he was taken hostage and forced to clear out ownerless garages, on the site of which German Eduardovich decided to build the best hotel in Penza. Gus falls under the subordination of Mikhalych, who also looks after the student nuclear physicist Funtik. He also works out his sins here.

name: 1583. Conte nuptial
story: Two old friends enroll in an adult university, looking for adventure, love and fun. What could go wrong?

name: 1584. Khajure Bro
story: Ulisses visits a vocational coach and ends up leaving the clinic with the power to discover people's true vocation with just one touch.

name: 1585. The Pickleball Murders
story: What if you got a second chance with the one who got away...in Paradise.

name: 1586. Nee Dhaarey Nee Katha
story: About how a family goes to celebrate the New Year in a place where there is no Internet.

name: 1587. Ranganayaka
story: Can't Let It Go is a film that explores the tense days before. during, and after the 2016 election through the experiences of a diverse group of New Yorkers .

name: 1588. Andrew Tate: Icon or Toxic? A Faking It Special
story: Ernests (70) and Alvine (64), two married postal workers, have developed a scheme to win a trip to Rome, but Alvine's rapidly progressing Alzheimer's disease complicates their scheme.

name: 1589. Nobody Leaves 'til Jesus Comes
story: A lonely sixty year old woman finds a new perspective on her life when an unexpected teenager appears on her doorstep. This troubled young man forces her to confront and question her personal history.

name: 1590. Tuesday
story: You are Alex Devine. You see and hear your friends and relatives come to you with their revelations, demands and grief, whilst you are unable to move or talk. Will your secrets be safe or compromised before it's all over?

name: 1591. Lump
story: Three young friends from Moscow are going to St. Petersburg to unwind. Unexpectedly for themselves, they buy a bar with their last savings and meet three guys who have one secret. A confrontation ensues, full of intrigue and unexpected twists. Will the girls be able to achieve success, or will they have to return to Moscow with nothing?

name: 1592. The Sweet Life
story: In Anthony Rodia's first stand up special, "Totally Relatable" is a comedic journey exploring the chaos of parenting, marital spats, and grappling with societies stupidity. Anthony navigates the absurdities of daily life, being raised by immigrant parents, and trying to uphold an old school way of raising kids.

name: 1593. Svetlyachok
story: 25 years after the events of the first film Psycho Ape, Nancy and Dr Zoomis have settled down into a quiet life. But when bodies start piling up again will the banana be pointed back at the supposedly reformed simian?

name: 1594. The Roast of Have A Word
story: It took a lockdown to unlock their hearts. In this award-winning romantic comedy, the solitary residents in a Los Angeles apartment building suddenly find themselves forced to rely on each other during the California stay-at-home. They are about to learn a lot about themselves as well as their rather unusual neighbors.

name: 1595. My Love from Another Land
story: When a 73-year-old widow is forced to depend on the care of her 5 busy adult children after an injury, she begins to question the meaning of family love.

name: 1596. Barbarian
story: Henry is a slacker floating through young adulthood earning a measly income from selling his body as a human punching bag. Meanwhile he wonders if there is more to his stagnating existence than the punches life throws at him.

name: 1597. Kunddala Puranam
story: Comedian Langston Kerman talks parenting a top-tier baby, teaching mean teens and managing his mother-in-law's dating apps in this hilarious special.

name: 1598. My Boyfriend Is a Sex Worker
story: 1954. The year since Joseph Stalin died. The whole country, and every Soviet person, is waiting for the unknown. A terrible, long, long, but one way or another, familiar era has ended. And no one knows what will happen next. And through this huge country, frozen in anticipation of an unclear future, a little boy, Mishka Chereyskiy, rides.

name: 1599. Especial Este
story: A businesswoman seeks spiritual guidance from being promiscuous. Her friend's pastor prays for her, leading to an unexpected turn in her romantic life. Starring Robert Ri'chard, Nicole "Hoopz" Alexander, Patrice Lovely, is known as Ma, and Ms. Hattie.

name: 1600. iKHlaas
story: A family comes together when nothing goes to plan on their roller-coaster ride Eid holiday (in Abu Dhabi).

name: 1601. Life with Quincy 3
story: 4 best friends goes on a vacation to a cabin. The unexpected happens. One of there friends have it in for them.

name: 1602. Chinatown Chacha
story: In this dark comedy, a genuinely nice guy's quest for love takes a twisted turn when he falls for the enigmatic and alluring Jennifer.

name: 1603. Salvation
story: A woman is living the best phase of her life, until she discovers that someone has turned her biggest secret into the plot of a primetime soap opera, where she is the villain.

name: 1604. Astral Plane Drifter
story: A coming-of-age dramedy about dating, career goals, and finding yourself.

name: 1605. Operation White Elephant
story: When Stewart Berwick flocks to the woods to direct his first feature film, his eccentric crew suffers through an intense shoot.

name: 1606. The Hutong Cowboy
story: In the midst of a creative crisis after years of making short films, a group of friends foolishly endeavor on a way to break out of their seemingly hopeless situation: make their first feature film with no money, credibility, or talent.

name: 1607. The Influencer
story: Six aspiring filmmakers leave home to pursue their dreams of making a movie, facing challenges and uncertainties along the way.

name: 1608. Hello Pot
story: Stefania, a budding actress, runs a blog attracting fans like aspiring star Aleks, student Masha, techie Tima, and enterprising Vanya. When Gennadiy the pony, starring in Stefania's film, is kidnapped, she turns to her fans for help.

name: 1609. Here We Go
story: Watch when a live social media carjacking attempt by the Apes goes hilariously wrong, Maurice seizes their gun and phone, live-streaming an epic humiliation that sets off a wild chain of events.

name: 1610. 12 Baes of Christmas
story: Six friends. One last epic summer adventure. Join a group of friends, who go on a vacation in La Union and encounter new experiences as they hang out with girls and party.

name: 1611. Adam Bol
story: Una brillante científica y psicoterapeuta prueba su "Elixir del Amor" en dos de sus pacientes, quienes se ven involucrados en una serie de desagradables efectos secundarios al tratar de encontrar el amor verdadero a través de la píldora.

name: 1612. El Maleka
story: It's summer vacation, but two high schoolers have been instructed to clean the (empty) swimming pool. As they sweep the pool, they initially discuss school life, love and makeup. But it isn't long before their worries begin to overflow and their thoughts intersect.

name: 1613. Saideira
story: Roxii, a queer hopeless romantic, just wants to be loved and treated the way boys do girls. A string of boys and men inform Roxii's view of sex and identity in late aughts Las Cruces, New Mexico.

name: 1614. Micha denkt groß
story: Young Nico seems to have everything clear, but life will teach him that he is very tangled

name: 1615. Papu mame zaverni
story: A cockroach-man Mute faces a dastardly puppeteer and saves his tone-deaf city with beer.

name: 1616. Zombie Anonymous
story: In an alternate world where assisted death is expected, private clinics profit off dignity. Maria Eugénia awaits her procedure, but it might not go as she expected.

name: 1617. Down Town
story: EXPERIENCE THE POWER PACKED ACTION TOUCHING MULTI GENRE'S. OVERCOMING THE EVIL ACTS, HOW JOHNNY HELPS THE VILLAGE PEOPLE WITH BREATHTAKING HOOK DRIVES AUDIENCE OF CLASS AND MASS INTO ANOTHER WORLD

name: 1618. Wieczór kawalerski
story: It deals with the events that develop after Mehmet, who is a diseased person, has the illusion that she has a week to live

name: 1619. Bed & Breakfast
story: The film follows life of a mortuary van driver, 3 college students and 2 police men who come across a bag full of money. The film depicts no matter whatever route one takes to fulfill their desire, at the end they get whatever is written.

name: 1620. Cinema Pichodu
story: Stavros is a somewhat unsuccessful filmmaker who teaches screenwriting at a film school in Athens, the birthplace of philosophy. Philosophizing in his own way as well, he asks the scripts to have a meaning, to have something to say and not just to tell a story. Thus, he has only a few students in his class. He loses his job just as his 19-year-old daughter comes from the island where she lives with her mother to stay with him in Athens to prepare for her university entrance exams. But she is not sure what she wants to do with her life and is searching for some deeper meaning. Stavros decides to write down all his thoughts about deeper meaning in a book. Despite his great financial need, he refuses the offer of a friend of his, a famous actress, to work on her soap opera, in order to concentrate on his philosophical book. Unfortunately, this is of no interest to any serious publisher, as he himself is completely irrelevant to academia. He is forced to pay a petty crook publisher himself to get his book published, because he thinks he has something to say. But it seems that his book is not of interest to readers either, since it remains unclaimed. Debt-ridden, he asks for a job on the soap opera, but they've found another director. Now impoverished, he moves around in deprived areas, full of refugees, where he finds unexpected support from a Moldovan sex worker, a former philosophy student, who was forced to give up her philosophical studies in her country, due to poverty. She seems very interested in his ideas, and thus his book finds its first reader. Still, he has to pay back his debts.

name: 1621. Jerry
story: Nine-year-old Leni and childlike intellectual Marcel, who is 23, kick around Bucharest in a joyous adventure, unruffled by the dark sides of life.

name: 1622. Výjimecný stav
story: The story of a young alien exploration who is being trapped by something can't be explained. Only by a leap of destiny, everything flips out for a young terrestrial to be completely insanely crazy in love by a foreign girl visiting town.

name: 1623. Hijo de familia
story: Savannah is 40 and reflecting on how becoming a young mother and wife robbed her of experiencing all that life has to offer. The kids have left for college, and she has separated from her husband.

name: 1624. Son Bir Tatil
story: The troubadour and his impostor friends - a Dog, a Cat, a Donkey and a narcissistic Rooster - teamed up to accomplish the feat. The wandering musicians, led by a new leader, will rally again to bring laughter and joy back to the gloomy streets of Bremen. First of all, they must make the King's daughter laugh, but meeting the Princess threatens a dangerous adventure. There are insidious enemies, intrigues and traps against the Troubadour and his friends, but you have to fight for love. And then the Princess ran away from the palace. In one tangle there are criminal schemes of Robbers, intrigues of a Detective, whims and secrets of the royal family, but cheerful musicians with an indefatigable Troubadour will make everyone dance to their tune. What are the Bremen Town musicians willing to do for the sake of the feat?

name: 1625. The Love Buzz
story: A desperate artistic director aims to revive his struggling theater with off-the-wall stage productions, all the while losing sight of why he chose this life in the first place.

name: 1626. Operation Portugal 2 - La vie de chateau
story: A retired secret agent happens across the mahjong collection of his late comrade-in-arms. He invites his three childhood friends to play, but when they start the game, they are sent on a real-life quest to find the "Golden Relic". The quest turns back time, making everyone young again. Determined to right some wrongs from the past during this journey, they deepen their friendship and learn new things along the way.

name: 1627. Fallen Leaves, Broken Lighters
story: Sophiya, a stunning young woman, is romantically involved with the affluent Turk, Hüseyin, without knowledge of his marital status. Sophiya's path crosses with Azamat, a hopeful immigrant from Kazakhstan who arrived in Istanbul years ago.

name: 1628. The Best Day of Your Life
story: A fencing athlete and aspiring soldier becomes entangled in a crisis involving his brother, manipulated by a sinister organization. This group triggers the "Code : Hunt" to eliminate a team accountable for the enigmatic murders.

name: 1629. Ben and Suzanne: A Reunion in 4 Parts
story: Elsabe, a widow in her 80s, and her three elderly friends embark on a hilarious road trip across the Karoo to experience a meteor shower in Sutherland. But they have to outsmart her overprotective son, who is hot on their tail.

name: 1630. Una fottuta bugia
story: On the day he plans to leave Nigeria for a new life abroad, Mezu discovers he's trapped in a time loop. His colleague Kamsi is in the same predicament. Together with their friends Tobe, Wasiu, and Sola, they must unite to break free.

name: 1631. Yashan yev Leonid Brezhnevy
story: Necip suffered a blow to his head as a result of a traffic accident and as a result of this blow, he suffers from memory loss. After checking their identity information, their relatives are notified. After a short while, the headman of the village, Sevket, and village people Selim and Hayati come to the hospital.

name: 1632. The Great Divide
story: Neang Neath was accused by the villagers of being involved with the bandits after her husband went to hide. Leader Vong attempted to assault her until she died, while Dao was hiding until he was victorious.

name: 1633. Killcon
story: The story of two best friends, Fish and Rex. After Fish crosses a local gang member, they strike a deal for their lives. Time is running out, just one problem. The dead girl in the living room, and they are being watched. Now they must figure out how to ditch the body, do the deal and save their lives. Join our two bumbling, yet lovable heroes on an adventure. Full of friendship, debauchery, necrophilia and rubber duckies.

name: 1634. Get Over Yourself
story: Arjun is a sincere cop and was kept under suspension for 6 months. After 6 months, when Dharma is going to contest as MLA in General elections, Arjun uses his full force along with a high plan of action and will be posted in the same Constituency for election protocol where he puts Dharma out of the MLA race. The conflict is How Dharma will uses his political support and money in his constituency for winning the race and how Arjun puts Dharma out of the MLA Race.

name: 1635. Local Sarakku
story: It tells the story of of an average middle-class boy who wants to become a successful singer in his life despite having obstacles in his way.

name: 1636. Blue Boy
story: The true story of a young heir from a wealthy family, who evolves from a hard-headed kid into an ambitious man as he embraces his luxurious lifestyle and battles rivals to earn his title as the most daring playboy of his era.

name: 1637. Can't Knock the Hustle
story: A hunter returns home to North Carolina with a mysterious green case. Following the death of his mother, he moves back into the family home where his mind begins to disintegrate. Stalked by voices and visions, guided by disquiet, hand written riddles and strange visitors further complicate an already splintering mind. A cable man, a mummified cat, zealous neighbors, and a killer swirl through this darkly comic southern gumbo.

name: 1638. The 9th Movie
story: A stand-up special from comedian Rachel Feinstein.

name: 1639. From Christmas, with Love
story: Liu Yonggan, a delivery boy known as "Shapingba Bolt", gathered 30 "thugs" to form a loser football team called "Dockers". They fought back and finally defeated the Warriors International Team and won the Eternal Bowl Championship.

name: 1640. Mind Body & Soul
story: Zhanna is an unusual housewife; she can read minds, move objects and influence people's minds. But she uses her superpower exclusively for personal purposes. One day she falls into the hands of the intelligence services and becomes a special intelligence agent. While carrying out one of her missions to clean up the top of organized crime, Zhanna is captured. There she has the opportunity to lead a squad of teenagers with very unusual superpowers and turn them into real superheroes.

name: 1641. Manasa Vacha
story: The cynical Permian official Viktor Letaev oversees road construction and is used to always getting his way. He knows and loves his job, but is not interested in anything else. His credo: "I chopped firewood, I had no time for these Chekhovs and Pasternaks of yours, because everyone needs firewood, and you can't warm a house with art." But the cynical worldview changes when culture and art become a new vector for the development of the region. Now, in order to sit in the chair of an official, he will have to study the cultural heritage of the Perm Territory. To help himself, he takes lessons from art history teacher Marina Nikolaevna. Will she be able to ennoble an uncultured official?

name: 1642. Just Nesh: Self Served
story: Jai works as a wholesaler of chicken eggs and has met a beautiful lady named Puteri. She asks him to deliver eggs to her house every Thursday. When some village chaps who had peeped into her house and saw that she consumes the eggs to maintain her beauty, they tried to warn Jai that she is not human, but he refuses to believe them.

name: 1643. Cooking in Yesterday's Grease
story: Trigga is on the verge of losing his restaurant. He must come up with $30,00 over the weekend or the landlord will take his building. What will he do?

name: 1644. Inga Naan Thaan Kingu
story: 10 years from now a virus more deadly and more contagious than anything we've ever seen decimates all the world's living creatures. Facing a total extinction event a brilliant geneticist named Dr Jonathan Figg discovers a miracle vaccine that is fast tracked into production, saving the final remnants of humanity. Unfortunately there's one side effect - the vaccine completely erases all memory of surfing from the human mind. With no idea what they're supposed to be doing with their lives the world's best surfers aimlessly wander off into what's left of society. Surfing is doomed. Now it's up to the Surf God Hughie to pull together a team of former greats - guys who dominated the riding of ocean waves - in a last ditch effort to save surfing. Can this bunch of forgotten outcasts work together to create the Greatest Surf Movie in the Universe triggering the populations memories of mondo-tubes, full-rail carves and giant rotating airs? Or are we destined to become a pack of horrendously strook land-lubbing kooks? Join X3 World Champion Surfer Mick Fanning along with cult favourites Craig Anderson, Mason Ho, Griffin Colapinto, Jack Freestone and Matt Wilkinson on their quest to make The Greatest Surf Movie in the Universe. Featuring stop motion animation, life-like figurines and voice-overs done by the athletes TGSMITU is a special effects action comedy unlike any surf film ever made.

name: 1645. Eksie Perfeksie
story: German and Lera are preparing for the wedding. The groom is going to give his beloved a car, but the car dealership insists on taking her for a test drive. The salon's salesman turns out to be Lera's ex-boyfriend, Maks, a reckless stuntman who is trying to make money on his stunt videos while working part-time at a car dealership.

name: 1646. L'BATAL
story: When acclaimed Adele Swan discovers that her young lover has squandered all her savings and is sleeping with a millennial, she knows it's showtime.

name: 1647. Supply Side Jesus
story: Mansarra is a specific species of rice. According to legend, it doesn't sprout alone; its seeds are typically mixed with other rice species before planting. However, this film declares the existence of independent Mansarra.

name: 1648. I Need Your Love
story: Lovers Kostya and Masha decide to get married. But immediately problems arise with relatives. Kostya's father is a retired military man, a strong-willed Russian man who plans to rent the House of Officers for a family celebration, invite all his relatives up to the fifth generation and celebrate according to the traditions of a Russian feast.

name: 1649. Headwind
story: "Miss Merkel - Ein Uckermark-Krimi 2" is a crime comedy feature film on RTL Deutschland. It's the second part of Miss Merkel - Ein Uckermark-Krimi (2023).

name: 1650. For Regn
story: A drug shipment arrives in Madrid, turning the lives of several characters upside down, as they struggle to resist the lure of easy money.

name: 1651. Doce Família
story: Four friends reminisce about their legacy after the wake of their friend's passing. Revelatory private affairs force them to deal with life choices that tangle them closer together in a way they never expected.

name: 1652. Grimmwood
story: The music industry becomes a battlefield when ancient strategist Kongming is transported from historical China to modern Japan. He'll use military tactics to turn his new friend Eiko into a music star, and together they'll take the party hotspot of Shibuya by storm.

name: 1653. Paraagan
story: It is a film that comments on the common youth of the village to the big political leader. a political satire can be said to be a film that comments on politics and society through comedy.

name: 1654. Baby boom czyli Kogel Mogel 5
story: Hector Soberon, fakes his death in order to avoid his problems. It only complicates things when people find out he is still alive.

name: 1655. Blue World
story: Three senior residents of a nursing home embark on an unexpected adventure after discovering a money laundering scheme.

name: 1656. Baby Bird
story: A group of friends attend a house party. Waiting through the doors is a wild night, an ex-girlfriend, and nigga zombies.

name: 1657. When Magic Hurts
story: Phil Wang riffs on reheated rice, octopus intelligence and the importance of fact-checking in this special filmed at Shakespeare's Globe in London.

name: 1658. National Theatre at Home: The Hot Wing King
story: The Grinch has to settle the score with Santa, so he decides to take a different approach.

name: 1659. Lyubov zla
story: Heartbroken after losing the love of his life, a young man makes a series of unsuccessful attempts to take his own life.

name: 1660. SangharshYoddha Manoj Jarange Patil
story: In What a Day Before Christmas, Nathan and Naomi are at odds about the direction of their marriage and Nathan's reluctance to get in the Christmas spirit. Naomi tasks Nathan with spending the holiday with her parents or else. Nathan agrees and embarks on an unforgettable trip with his cousin, Keith and a very peculiar Uber driver. Nathan must be at his in laws by Christmas Eve to avoid being in the dog house. Just when you think things can't any worse they do. Nathan and his crew seem to have the worst luck and with each passing hour, it doesn't appear to be in the cards for him to make it to his in laws on time.

name: 1661. Dracu Ra
story: Supermarket worker Kal meets Cambridge graduate Sarah. All so habibi, except for the financial catastrophe Kal causes their community.

name: 1662. V banyu!
story: The Snow Queen and Santa Claus were once old friends who learned the magic of cold together. But their paths parted when the Snow Queen, envious of her friend's strength, stole a magical artifact from which Santa Claus drew his power and created magic. The wizard was able to defeat the sorceress with some difficulty and imprisoned her in an ice prison. Thousands of years later, nowadays, the boy Yura finds the ice staff of the Snow Queen at the New Year's fair and unwittingly frees her. Returning to the modern world, she decides to take revenge on her sworn friend and comes up with an insidious plan that will freeze the whole world on New Year's Eve. For this purpose, she kidnaps a boy and takes him to the ice kingdom. To prevent her machinations and save not only Yura, but also the whole world, Santa Claus will need the help of the sorceress Baba Yaga, Ivan Tsarevich, Maria the artificer and other magical creatures. A new, incredible adventure awaits them.

name: 1663. I Brake for Caterpillars
story: The story begins in the universe known as Realm 6.2, a pet realm ruled by the Dark Lord Chin-Chin, whom can convert beings with a low Chromosome count such as humans into Lycra entities. Chin-Chin goes on to use his powers as a virus and infects many Realms. Frank manages to survive the lycrapocalypse and seeks refuge in an apartment complex. Not long after the end of the lycrapocalypse, Frank becomes a known adventurer throughout the Omniverse, exploring many realms and meeting many friends along the way.

name: 1664. Christmas Cards
story: Former Stepdad, Terry Miller, on the run from the law after escaping prison. Along side his estranged Stepson, Kyle, they must learn to work together in order to evade the law and stop Kyle's mother from marrying a new man.

name: 1665. Vovó Ninja
story: Two former friends from the Marine Corps must reconcile and settle their old feud to battle a corrupt property developer.

name: 1666. Look at Me
story: A dark comedy about a no name wanna be Rhode Island gangster by the name of Nick Sargenti and his goofy group of untalented misfits. The story focuses around a documentary filmmaker following Nick and is group of wannabe gangster's.

name: 1667. Youn'G
story: A Christmas miracle happens in a home for children without parents - Zlati, a famous face from the small screen, showman, and host of "Golden Show" arrives. He has taken on the noble initiative "Take Me Home" - a call for kindness and compassion. Zlati invites little Yan to visit his own home for Christmas. For one day, the child will be in the spotlight and learn a lot about the false glamour of success.

name: 1668. Retro Therapy
story: Ten-year-old Lusha's father, failed writer Boris Kolechkin, works as a sales consultant for Lusha's mother Alina. She once preferred him to Sergey Amiantov, on whom the fate of her business now depends. Alina, Lusha and Boris, at Amiantov's invitation, go to his New Year's carnival. There a duel begins between the men. Lusha helps her father as best she can. The Kolechkins are unaware that the stolen ring of the ancient Egyptian queen Nefertiti was hidden in the half-eaten hot dog that the stray dog Karuzo gave to their dog Kristi. The thieves of a priceless ring are organizing a hunt for Kristi in the absence of the owners of the Kolechkins' house. They are confronted by Karuzo, who is in love with Kristi, and who is sheltered by the family.

name: 1669. Rosetta Stoned
story: A small group of hunters come to earth chasing sentient worms from space. They must stop these parasites before they take over all of the inhabitants of earth. Teaming up with some of the locals may be the only way to survive until morning.

name: 1670. Chor Chor
story: At the threshold of fantasy and magical realism, Barbara and Victoria explore two opposing worldviews. Navigating dreamlike landscapes, they seek to fulfill their dreams without fit into the mold.

name: 1671. Powerball
story: Ruminations on the life of actor Mick Innes: joy, failure, success, heartache, heart attack, reinvention and the love of his life.

name: 1672. Maa Da Sohna
story: After 10 years of being in a coma Tony wakes up and realizes he's not a kid anymore and has responsibilities. - A funny comedy movie.

name: 1673. Ghostlight
story: Milton had a dream. Now he has a cafe. In a washed-up, rundown seaside town, surrounded by his father's collection of silent movie memorabilia and a mountain of debt. Until Jenna arrives with a second-hand camera and a crazy idea.

name: 1674. Slasher Days of Summer
story: Heart Brakers is a magical realism drama that explores how one couple struggles to overcome the dark side of love through parallel universes.

name: 1675. Amor Platónico
story: Tyler Tate, a washed up actor whose life has been ravaged by alcoholism, retreats to a small motel near his Ohio hometown after losing his job and family. Overwhelmed by despair, Tate finds himself in a fog of hopelessness until he starts volunteering at a local theater. Teaching acting to a group of troubled teens, he begins to see a vision of a better future. Through faith and connection, Tate discovers that God's plan for his life is far greater than he ever imagined.

name: 1676. Master Dragon
story: A classic comedy film produced in the USA with the participation of Armenian actors and professional American creative and production teams. The film takes place in the United States of America. The script is an adaptation of Claude Monet's French comedy play "Oscar", which touches on subjects of such manifestations of love as long-forgotten love and the difficult choice of a life partner. These are often accompanied by lies that try to destroy human relationships, and the heroes of the film "Koko" are no exception in this matter. Seemingly small lies create difficult and at the same time funny situations for the characters. The characters speak Armenian grammatically. The filmmakers expect the audience to leave the theater with bright and colorful emotions, while, of course, thinking about life at the same time.

name: 1677. Osobennosti natsionalnoy bolnitsy
story: When K-Chill and West get away with the money they find themselves deeper into the underworld. They are on a new mission to expand and will not let anything get in their way. What they don't know is what troubles are waiting in their path. Can they work there way out or get stuck in the cycle.

name: 1678. 23 Horas
story: french ambassador by an order of the french government goes to an italian island in order to culturally colonialize it, but someone comes in between and the plans changes.

name: 1679. Uranus Attacks
story: Revolves around children's mindset when they are mistreated by their parents.

name: 1680. Critic
story: Five participants who have never been tested before will be tested in this Christmas special released on December 20, 2024.

name: 1681. The Holy Man Comeback
story: The film, dedicated to all living Romanis, tells the story of what happened after a murder committed in a Romani neighborhood.

name: 1682. Lockdown Lagna
story: Gregory and Matilda take a weekend trip out to small village town, Chama, New Mexico with the self-imposed mission to decide if they'll be leaving back home as a couple only to be swept up by the mysterious happenings of the town.

name: 1683. Sugar Baby 2: ¿Papi paga?
story: At the peak of her mid-life crisis, a full time mom will do whatever it takes to conquer the friendship and admiration of her teenage daughter, even facing her deepest fears by joining a beauty contest in a summer resort.

name: 1684. Por tus muertos
story: Three actresses go to the film festival together. The successful Adéla will present her new film. The burnt-out Ema goes to support her and carefree Sona just wants to enjoy parties. But their friendships and careers are put to the test.

name: 1685. You'll Be Hurt When I'm Done
story: A video store owner plans a sting operation when he comes to believe that one of his regulars is a notorious serial killer known as The Fiend.

name: 1686. Babu (No.1 Bullshit Guy)
story: Official Grisha from the Committee for the Protection of Cultural Heritage Sites has an ideal plan: to carefully kidnap his boss on New Year's Eve in order to pull off a deal with yet another shopping center in the city center himself. Grisha has foreseen everything, and it's hard to imagine what could go wrong.

name: 1687. Gap Lai Chi Bau
story: An anthology web series, aggregated into a feature, based on the mysterious stories of dreams and dreamers.

name: 1688. Lakeview
story: A family of four sets off for a summer vacation by the sea in the camper van. Even though the Adriatic is within reach, the journey might just take longer than expected.

name: 1689. The Legend of Crick Foot
story: After Kyle and Jake got Kidnapped, Kyle finds out that Ed and Denny Tries to steal The Last Emerald to Doom the World. Kyle and Jake are having a quest to Stop them for stealing The Last Emerald.

name: 1690. Cuñados
story: Two friends set out to Vegas on a bizarre bachelor party where they learn how to be male strippers in hopes of feeling sexy in their own skin.

name: 1691. Bob a Bobek ve filmu: Na stope Mrkvojeda
story: Three boys-Vikram, Siddharth, and Aayush-join a prestigious hostel. Vikram follows tradition, Siddharth navigates independence, and Aayush, an orphan, strives for success as they compete for a spot on the wall of fame?

name: 1692. The Haunted Granny
story: Here is a synopsis of the Pakistani film "Hum Tum Aur Woo" (HTAW): HTAW is a Situational comedy film that revolves around the lives of three friends, Fawad (Junaid Khan), Zafar (Saad Khan), and Raja Yasir( Neni Abbasi). The story follows their journey as they navigate love, relationships, and friendship. Fawad, a charming and witty guy, falls in love with Sara (Amna Ilyas), but their relationship is put to the test when Woo, a quirky and eccentric friend, gets involved. The film explores themes of love, friendship, and growing up, with plenty of humor and wit. With its light-hearted tone and relatable characters, HTAW is a heartwarming and entertaining ride. Movie keeps you entertained with the dialogues and the story throughout 100 minutes.

name: 1693. Nothing Unusual
story: 2 recent college graduates find themselves at a cross roads trying to figure out what career path they want to take. They refuse to work a boring regular 9-5 job, and learn they can make a killer living simply off reselling sneakers.

name: 1694. Shanghai Story
story: Eddie Green performs his first comedy special in his hometown of Riviera Beach, Florida. Jokes on the church and TMI stories of his sexual conquests...all with his pastor in attendance.

name: 1695. Moyo sobache delo
story: Lily is an office executive with her life still in shambles. Dante just longs for the days when sinning was much simpler. One wild evening. The Devil wears a black velvet sports jacket and skinny jeans in this outrageous dark comedy film.

name: 1696. Couple in the Woods
story: Ernst drives to the mountains to commit suicide in front of an idyllic panorama, but all his attempts fail because he suddenly gets harassed by a person who looks exactly like him.

name: 1697. Iyer in Arabia
story: Five girls in their thirties reunite for a bachelorette party. During 24 hours in a rented house, comedic, tender, and dramatic moments test their friendship, ultimately bringing them closer together despite their differences.

name: 1698. Market Mahalakshmi
story: Von is a young man put in a situation to grow up really quickly. The pressure of this challenge sends him searching for answers. His family has problems helping him find his way so he turns to his God sister Peaches.

name: 1699. Bernadette will töten
story: Jasmine learns she has a royal twin named Sofia. Both were lost at birth, but both want to experience one another's lives.

name: 1700. OMG: O Manchi Ghost
story: Beni and Reuven, childhood friends and brothers-in-law, work together as TV technicians. They are called for a simple repair job in a place they find abandoned and unlocked, with the door wide open. Inside, they are surprised to find a dead body, unaware that the crime scene they have stumbled upon belongs to a known criminal. They make every possible mistake, turning themselves into the prime suspects of the murder case. From this point forward, they try to stay away from both the crime family and the police.

name: 1701. Dragons on the Hill
story: Three friends embark on a quest to find girlfriends but planning the perfect date takes an unexpected turn, revealing that love's path is filled with surprises.

name: 1702. Puffing Iron
story: The love story of Sofia Von Sydov (known as the Flying Princess), heiress of a large circus family, and Andrea Parodi, scion of a wealthy naval entrepreneur, in search of happiness and their place in the world.

name: 1703. Tom and Jerry
story: The once friendly and loving Gureev family finds itself on the verge of divorce. Spouses Olga and Sergey have moved away from each other, and children Anton and Nastya worry about their parents. Sergey, a fashion photographer, receives an assignment to fly to an exhibition. He is trying to cancel the business trip because it is Nastya's birthday. Olga, once again disappointed in her husband's actions, is ready to file for divorce... But eight-year-old Nastya, their daughter, buys a trip to Armenia for the whole family with the donated money. Fun adventures await the Gureev family, including an immersion in the flavor of a local wedding, which is celebrated for just 7 days and 7 nights. They will also pass their own tests, which will help them understand what is most valuable and important in this life.

name: 1704. Ma part de Gaulois
story: From the creators who won Best Comedy Special at the 2024 Canadian Screen Awards, Rez Comedy is the first all-Indigenous stand-up comedy documentary feature, showcasing nine diverse and talented Indigenous comedians.

name: 1705. Inazuma Eleven the Movie: Prologue to the New Heroes
story: Caught between a thankless job with cruel co-workers and a surreal home life consisting of video games, fast food and insomnia, Abe finds out that he has a higher purpose. No matter what, violence is never the answer.

name: 1706. Koresha
story: Seymour and his friends, Corrina and Wally, are desperate to avoid the vampire hunters, while securing a constant source of blood that does not involve Seymour attacking humans. However, as Seymour gets hungrier he must learn to control his urges. Strange circumstances abound as he also endeavors to keep the particulars of his new existence from his family. Seymour has to work his way out of many uncomfortable situations in his new altered life. Seymour finds some comfort after his abduction by the Agency of the Supernatural Rehabilitation Services. A world wise werewolf, named Chester, is sent to guide him through this transition. Chester is charmingly unrefined and is keen to keep an eye on the unfortunate Seymour as he knows how humans can be to those who are different. A new threat arises when Seymour's condition is inadvertently revealed to a fairy (displaying no characteristics normally associated with being a fairy). Lark Cedarcreek, is tall and usually bears no visible wings. Far from being a gentle, nymph like creature, he bears a greater resemblance to Boris Karlof. It is revealed that while the blood of a fairy can allow a vampire to walk in the light of day, fairies are dangerous to vampires because vampire blood is like a drug to a fairy. Seymour is lovable, and naive. His friends are loyal. It is an adventure through the surprises experienced by a newly turned, fairly innocent vampire to find acceptance of himself, friends, family and survival with his new life.

name: 1707. La Tercera Edad
story: Gandhi an orphan leads his life doing all wrong things accompanied by his childhood friend Quarter. Gold Reddy a well known rowdy of that village causes more trouble to both Gandhi. Gandhi avenge Gold Reddy.

name: 1708. Vidente por Acidente
story: After several failed attempts at finding the right man, Oluwatemilorun,, a young, independent and hardworking lady gets frustrated by her mother's constant complaints. Mrs Ngozie wants her daughter to find and marry a man as soon as possible. This prompts her to set up dates with multiple men for her daughter, which all fail woefully for some flimsy excuse or the other. Meanwhile, Paul, a seasoned womanizer, jumps from one girl to the other with no plans of stopping at all. His best friend, Idongesit, would support him under any circumstance... Fed up with all her mother's continuous pressure to find a man, Obiageli falls into the hands of Richard, who tricks her with a fake marriage proposal just so he sleep with her. After Richards gets his way, Obiageli finds out he was married and is told to stay away from Richard. In an unexpected turn of events, Paul, all dressed and dashing out meets a delicate situation where Oluwatemilorun is standing on a building, about to commit suicide due to the heartbreak she has experienced from Richard. Paul is forced to intervene; to persuade her to revoke her decision, one thing leads to another, and Paul find himself promising to marry Oluwatemilorun should she choose to stay alive. After taking the knee and proposing to Oluwatemilorun, Paul is left dumbfounded when Oluwa trips and falls off the building. Paul runs off, relieved that he didn't have to deal with such a situation anymore... Unfortunately, waking up in what is supposed to be a beautiful morning, Paul is confronted with the ghost of Oluwatemilorun, his new wife. Frist, it is utter shock, then denial and fear and panic set in as Paul tries to run away or get rid of his new spirit wife to no avail. He faints while trying to escape Obiageli and gets help from his friends, Idongesit, Somto and other well-wishers. When Paul explains his ordeal to his best friend, Idongesit takes him to a fake Pastor who makes excessive demands before he will help them. On getting to the house and realizing that Paul wasn't joking about the ghost, both the pastor and Idongesit run off, leaving Paul to himself again... However, Oluwa and Paul get into a heated argument, during which she now understands that it is impossible for man and ghost to be together, she decides to help Paul get together with Somto, whom she has noticed Paul has chemistry with. Paul and Oluwa, now allies, help each other face their fears. Paul helps Oluwatemilorun make peace with her mother and in turn, Oluwa helps Paul get gifts for Somto. In the course of getting the gifts, Oluwa sees Richard's car, tells Paul about it. Paul then goes ahead to vandalize the car but is caught and given a beating by Richard who is far bigger in size and stronger than him. Somto gets worried about Paul's bruises when he goes to present her with the gifts he bought. But he quickly dismisses it as nothing. Telling her he beat up a guy. Oluwa encourages Paul to speak his mind to her again, for the second time. Sadly, Somto tells Paul she is already seeing someone, but is quite disappointed when Paul tells her he is good with her decision and doesn't being just friends like they were before. Immediately Somto leaves them alone, Oluwa assures him that Somto has feelings for him and is just waiting for Paul to fight for her. Paul and Oluwa are both taken aback when they see that Somto's date is none other than Richard. Paul has no choice but to reveal everything about Richard to her, which Somto later confirms for herself during her date with him. Somto comes back to thank Paul for saving her the disappointment, which finally brings them both to confessing their feelings for each other. As they both kiss, Oluwa slowly vanishes until we see her no more. Realizing this, Paul heaves a big sigh of relief and is happy that finally got who he has always wanted, Somto.

name: 1709. Aloha Also Means Goodbye
story: Two Concerned historians in the borough of West Chester try to save the Farmers and Mechanics building from being torn down and replaced like other buildings in town. The film will highlight parts of West Chester's history while telling a fictional narrative.

name: 1710. Novyy god v Beryozovke
story: A new adventure of Luccas Neto in medieval times.

name: 1711. Can't Let It Go
story: A mysterious chance encounter connects high schoolers from the 60s, 70s, 80s, and 90s with siblings from 2024 on their graduation day.

name: 1712. Ramana Avatara
story: A stuttering Don Giovanni will change his life: to receive an inheritance he will have to marry an unmarried woman. Born with a silver spoon, the protagonist will discover that true luck lies in love without a parachute.

name: 1713. A Postcard from Rome
story: The kids with their parents were ready to celebrate Curve Bro's 21st Birthday by giving his parents a punishment day.

name: 1714. Kinfolk
story: There is a village at the end of the world, where three brothers are being happily bored.

name: 1715. Sexagenarian
story: Sally feels disconnected from life until she is convinced by her psychiatrist and her friends that dating is the answer.

name: 1716. COMA
story: When a routine outing at work takes an unexpected turn, a group of young friends find themselves caught in the cross hairs of a ruthless politician and a mysterious assassin in a fast paced and high stakes race for survival.

name: 1717. Cingene Kizi Zeugma
story: Man is strangled in a park in Evosmos. Police officers Manos Kallidis and Petros Theodorou investigate, overcoming their differences, until they solve the case.

name: 1718. Bar MoskvaChiki
story: Verkhnekamsk. Lonely loser Sasha works as a security guard at an exchange office. His life "didn't happen," his dreams didn't come true, his family didn't work out. Sasha feels unnecessary and unhappy, and not being able to change anything, he gives up morally. But even here Sasha does not have the courage to complete the matter himself, he turns to an old friend - the husband of his ex-wife - for help.

name: 1719. Anthony Rodia Totally Relatable
story: Stas is a miner, not the most hardworking, but very charming. By chance, he ends up buried in a mine along with eco-activist Lena. Then he begins to hear a voice. Voice of the Earth. In her speeches, she speaks for the environment, and threatens that she will drown everyone if they don't listen to her. The problem is that only Stas hears her. And now he will have to very quickly convince the whole world that a) he is not a schizophrenic and b) he urgently needs to stop polluting the Earth, otherwise it will wash everyone away from its face.

name: 1720. Psycho Ape: Part II - The Wrath of Kong
story: Seeking adventure, a widower finds love in a walking club, but a hidden truth puts his blossoming romance with a spirited woman to the test. Finding love at 70 is no walk in the park.

name: 1721. A Wall Away
story: In The Empathizer, director Fred Le travels to Vietnam to explore why his mother refuses to return to the homeland she left. There, he interviews a number of Vietnamese expatriates who have made a living in Vietnam, including artists, athletes, business owners, and students. Each discusses the contradictions between what they learned about Vietnam during their own Western upbringings and their experiences in present-day Vietnam. It might appear, at first, that The Empathizer is leaning so heavily on the views of the young Viet kieu (the Vietnamese diaspora) who emigrated back to Vietnam, but Le eventually returns to the source of why this film exists. And when he does, The Empathizer finds its emotional and moral center. Aptly titled, The Empathizer pushes the audience to consider the diverse viewpoints and experiences of the various Vietnamese diaspora approaches to Vietnam. It blends humor and gravity in articulating the lasting effects of division, suspicion and animosity borne out of war, forced migration, and politics. The film speaks directly to the children of Vietnamese refugees who seek to empathize with the tribulations of their parents, but often cannot fully grasp the effects of displacement-induced trauma. Highlighting the rift between generations, The Empathizer pushes the audience to explore ways to build empathy and understanding.

name: 1722. Face Off 7: One Wish
story: Supernatural creature blogger Jareth Grass is sucked into the world of fantastical urban creatures and discovers his family's magical past.

name: 1723. Jellyfish
story: The life of 17-year-old Eva is boring and uninteresting, she feels invisible. But everything changes when she accuses a former famous singer of sexual harassment and turns into a national heroine - "a girl who was not afraid to tell the truth."

name: 1724. Langston Kerman: Bad Poetry
story: A modern era boy visits hometown for his sister's wedding, soon discovering his own proposal finalized with a girl he's never seen. Fighting against the family customs, his only mission is to at least see the face of his future wife-to-be.

name: 1725. Tayna Chyornoy Ruki
story: It is the story of Qanbar and Sanam, who are struggling with new challenges in their life together in the continuation of the previous episode.

name: 1726. Periodt
story: Ben is a widower who misses his wife Maggie, but finds solace in his weekly meetings with his actor son, Jason. On this day, Ben reveals to Jason that he has hired a prostitute, not for sexual favors, but simply for companionship.

name: 1727. Al Eid Eiden
story: You can take a young man out of the Caucasus, but never take the Caucasus out of a young man. Apparently, the Caucasian relatives of the Russified Ossetian thought so when they decided to help him, following the ancient tradition, to ride his St. Petersburg bride to the village. But what if, in the end, the wrong bride ends up in the car, the family learns David's main secret, and for all the guests who have gathered, the wedding will still need to be held? Then "Caucasian Bollywood" will come.

name: 1728. 4GUYS&ACABIN
story: Follows a headhunter from Sao Paulo who recruits an art director from Salvador, for a job interview. In a short time, their friendship turns into a casual friends-with-benefits relationship until they both fall in love.

name: 1729. Toxic
story: The Haunting of Lanquetot, set in present day Normandy France is an adrenaline fueled comedy horror of murder, human weakness and an historical love tale brought to life through one girls struggle, Chantilly, to escape her own limitations.

name: 1730. A Vilã das Nove
story: A successful woman's life is disrupted by her mother's decision to move away to write poetry.

name: 1731. Echoes of Dreams
story: REST AND RELAX is a film oddity about the anxieties of our time made by and starring artist/musicians Sook-Yin Lee and Dylan Gamble. Four stories explore life in the 21st century while surviving capitalism, sickness, and the internet.

name: 1732. When You Love June
story: In a prank gone wrong, Annie and Billy appear to have killed their friend, Jeff. As guests continue to arrive, the couple's attempts in hiding the body only seem to increase their body count. The Terrible Killers try to navigate the rest of their night without being caught, and without killing anyone else.

name: 1733. Loss of Essence
story: A reporter goes down into the NYC subway system to investigate the phenomenon of the subway shark.

name: 1734. Pink Is In: The Movie
story: Lisa, grandchild of late lawyer Robert, joins his former law office which is now run by Robert's successor Talia. They have to deal with a tenant who fails to pay rent and an old man who feels discriminated by a Vietnamese cafe owner.

name: 1735. Cast & Crew
story: A hapless journalist thinks she's found the perfect luxury home, until she discovers why the rent is so cheap: it's haunted by the previous owner.

name: 1736. Kallanmaarude Veedu
story: When Tiffany and Gabi become roommates, they both realize the other bears a secret: Gabi is bisexual. Tiffany is a cannibal.

name: 1737. Odna doma. Velikolepnaya pyatyorka
story: A queer woman in her late twenties continuously runs headfirst into an existential crisis over the course of a year.

name: 1738. Yall Drawn
story: A nihilist finds purpose when he rescues the 'Excalibur' of vintage bicycles from a garbage heap, but his renewed trajectory is threatened when a devious collector steals it, igniting a chase that could lead him back to meaning-or deeper into despair.

name: 1739. G! LU!
story: Anne is stupefied when her demented father Ludwig announces he has an illegitimate daughter (named Anne as well). This Anne will share his legacy or may even get all. But the first Anne won't accept that without a fight. Even Erik helps.

name: 1740. El Elixir del Amor
story: A filmmaker makes a movie in a way that's never been done before, leading to unimaginable results.

name: 1741. Swimming in a Sand Pool
story: A painfully narcissistic theater producer attempts to realize a delusional creative vision: a musical version of his favorite movie, SCREAM, with an accompanying documentary chronicling what he believes will be an iconic journey.

name: 1742. Hidden Flora
story: Good Luck Company, a place helps you realize all your dreams. Yao Ke and Jia Ling take the lead in building a professional team. No matter how outrageous your daydream is, they can turn "absurdity" into magic and make it come true.

name: 1743. Cupido confuso
story: The Ugandan tiger mafia kidnaps the son of prime minster of Israel. In order to rescue him, the State of Israel sends a pair of special commando fighters to Uganda, whose partnership was broken up by a bitter conflict in the past.

name: 1744. Bob's Hops
